'''牛津－阿斯利康2019冠状病毒病疫苗'''（{{lang-en|Oxford–AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine}}，簡稱：'''AZ疫苗'''、'''阿斯特捷利康疫苗'''、'''牛津疫苗'''，代号：'''AZD1222'''，[[商品名|商品名]]：{{lang|en|Vaxzevria}}<ref name="COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca EPAR" />、{{lang|en|Covishield}}<ref name="CA About"/><ref name="Covishield"/>）由[[英國|英國]][[牛津大學|牛津大學]]與[[阿斯利康製藥|阿斯利康製藥]]合作研發，以改良的非複製型黑猩猩[[病毒載體|腺病毒載體]]（ChAdOx1）為技術基礎，是一款針對[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]的預防[[2019冠状病毒病疫苗|疫苗]]<ref name="AU TGA decision">{{cite web|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca|url=https://www.tga.gov.au/apm-summary/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca|accessdate=2020-02-16|date=2021-02-16|work=Therapeutic Goods Administration|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318065117/https://www.tga.gov.au/apm-summary/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca|archivedate=2021-03-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，英國藥品及保健品管理局於2020年12月30日批准該款疫苗的緊急授權使用許可<ref name="英國批准牛津大學疫苗">{{cite news|title=英國批准牛津大學疫苗 元月4日開始施打|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202012300363.aspx|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=中央通訊社|date=2020-12-30|archivedate=2021-01-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126030353/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202012300363.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[歐洲藥品管理局|歐洲藥品管理局]]亦於2021年1月30日批准該款疫苗在[[歐盟|歐盟]]使用<ref name="歐盟批准使用阿斯利康疫苗">{{cite news|title=歐盟批准使用阿斯利康疫苗　第三款獲批疫苗|url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573145-20210130.htm|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=香港電台|date=2021-01-30|archivedate=2021-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421043438/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573145-20210130.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，該款疫苗於2021年2月15日獲[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]列入緊急使用清單<ref name="牛津疫苗列入世衛使用清單">{{cite news|title=世卫组织将两版牛津-阿斯利康疫苗列入紧急使用清单|url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/02/1078002|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=世界衛生組織|date=2021-02-15|archivedate=2021-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421043440/https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/02/1078002|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WHO: AZD1222">{{cite web |title=Interim recommendations for use of the ChAdOx1-S [recombinant] vaccine against COVID-19 (AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine AZD1222, SII Covishield, SK Bioscience) |url=https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/WHO-2019-nCoV-vaccines-SAGE_recommendation-AZD1222-2021.1/ |publisher=World Health Organization |accessdate=2021-04-29 |archive-date=2021-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618101655/https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/WHO-2019-nCoV-vaccines-SAGE_recommendation-AZD1222-2021.1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時成為[[COVAX|世衛組織全球疫苗分配計劃（COVAX）]]首種發放的疫苗<ref name="COVAX公布首轮疫苗分配计划">{{cite news|title=COVAX公布首轮疫苗分配计划|url=https://www.who.int/zh/news/item/02-03-2021-covax-publishes-first-round-of-allocations|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=世界衛生組織|date=2021-03-02|archive-date=2021-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211021113405/https://www.who.int/zh/news/item/02-03-2021-covax-publishes-first-round-of-allocations|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且在全球多國廣泛生產，在[[英國|英國]]、[[比利時|比利時]]、[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]<ref name="歐盟要求阿斯利康英國廠增產">{{cite news|title=新冠疫苗缺口巨大，歐盟憤怒要求阿斯利康英國工廠提高供應|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-55838487|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=BBC中文网|date=2021-01-28}}</ref>、[[意大利|意大利]]、[[印度|印度]]<ref name="印度代產阿斯利康疫苗">{{cite news|title=印度代產阿斯利康疫苗 或准運至英國接種|url=https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2712940/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%A2%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97+%E6%88%96%E5%87%86%E9%81%8B%E8%87%B3%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=信報|date=2021-02-16}}</ref>、[[韓國|韓國]]<ref name="牛津疫苗列入世衛使用清單"/>、[[日本|日本]]<ref name="日本藥廠生產1.2億劑">{{cite news|title=【阿斯利康疫苗】日本藥廠生產1.2億劑 全部Made in Japan|url=https://inews.hket.com/article/2900013/%E3%80%90%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%97%A5%E5%BB%A0%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A21.2%E5%84%84%E5%8A%91%20%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8Made%20in%20Japan|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=香港經濟日報|date=2021-03-12|archive-date=2021-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604225743/https://inews.hket.com/article/2900013/%E3%80%90%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%97%A5%E5%BB%A0%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A21.2%E5%84%84%E5%8A%91%20%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8Made%20in%20Japan|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[澳洲|澳洲]]及[[泰國|泰國]]等國都設有生產線<ref name="澳洲生產阿斯利康疫苗">{{cite news|title=探秘生产5000万剂阿斯利康疫苗的澳洲CSL制药厂|url=https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2021-02-12/covid-19-vaccine-oxford-astrazeneca-adenovirus-csl/13150340|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=ABC News|date=2021-02-12|archivedate=2021-02-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218092034/https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2021-02-12/covid-19-vaccine-oxford-astrazeneca-adenovirus-csl/13150340|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿斯利康疫苗在涵蓋2.4萬人的第三期臨床測試中，有效率平均達到70.4%，最高可達90%<ref name="stheadline-20201123">{{cite news|title=牛津新冠疫苗有效率達70% 向低成本易儲存邁出一大步|url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1930936/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E9%81%9470-%E5%90%91%E4%BD%8E%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%98%93%E5%84%B2%E5%AD%98%E9%82%81%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A5|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=頭條日報|date=2020-11-23|archivedate=2020-11-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130194556/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1930936/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E9%81%9470-%E5%90%91%E4%BD%8E%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%98%93%E5%84%B2%E5%AD%98%E9%82%81%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A5|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="牛津疫苗間隔三個月80%">{{cite news|title=牛津/阿斯利康新冠疫苗在两剂注射间隔三个月时 有效率可达80%--英国官员|url=https://cn.reuters.com/article/uk-vaccine-oxford-1231-idCNKBS295033|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=路透社|date=2020-12-31|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107153726/https://cn.reuters.com/article/uk-vaccine-oxford-1231-idCNKBS295033|dead-url=no}}</ref>，雖然有效率不及在同期發表第三期臨床測試報告的[[輝瑞疫苗|輝瑞疫苗]]及[[莫德納疫苗|莫德納疫苗]]，不過阿斯利康疫苗可於攝氏2度至8度的冰箱保存6個月<ref name="阿斯利康疫苗到底好不好">{{cite news|title=阿斯利康疫苗到底好不好？|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD/a-56773286|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=德國之聲|date=2021-03-04|archivedate=2021-03-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310193959/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD/a-56773286|dead-url=no}}</ref>，具有易於貯存及運輸的優點，而且價格低廉<ref name="新冠疫苗價格浮現">{{cite news|title=新冠疫苗價格浮現：中國產疫苗高定價Vs 美國政府全球大採購|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-54277046|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=BBC|date=2020-09-25|archivedate=2020-11-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126185348/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-54277046|dead-url=no}}</ref>，每劑只需3英鎊<ref name="牛津疫苗研發成功">{{cite news|title=牛津疫苗研發成功 三種疫苗各有優勢|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-55048528|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=BBC|date=2020-11-23|archivedate=2020-11-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124164306/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-55048528|dead-url=no}}</ref>，便於[[發展中國家|發展中國家]]推動大規模疫苗接種<ref name="人民的疫苗">{{cite news|title=人民的疫苗：慈善與牛津 – 阿斯利康疫苗|url=https://privatebank.jpmorgan.com/gl/zh-hk/insights/giving/the-peoples-vaccine-philanthropy-and-the-oxford-astrazeneca-vaccine|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=J.P. Morgan|date=2021-01-19|archivedate=2021-03-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330044239/https://privatebank.jpmorgan.com/gl/zh-hk/insights/giving/the-peoples-vaccine-philanthropy-and-the-oxford-astrazeneca-vaccine|dead-url=no}}</ref>。世衛組織表示阿斯利康製藥是唯一承諾不從事全球疫情牟利的疫苗開發商，阿斯利康疫苗也是唯一通過開放技術授權其他疫苗廠商參與生產提升產量的疫苗<ref name="UN-News">{{cite news|title=世卫组织：新冠疫苗的不平等情况“日益变得更加荒谬”|url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/03/1080722|accessdate=2021-03-24|work=聯合國新聞|date=2021-03-22|archivedate=2021-04-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401193705/https://news.un.org/zh/story/2021/03/1080722|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由世衛主導的全球疫苗分配計劃（COVAX）分發的疫苗，有90%是由[[印度血清研究所|印度血清研究所]]及韓國[[SK集團|SK生物製藥]]代工生產的阿斯利康疫苗<ref name="UN-News" />。

==技术==
牛津－阿斯利康COVID-19疫苗是一款以复制缺陷型黑猩猩[[腺病毒|腺病毒]]为载体<ref name="疫苗原理">{{cite news|title=拯救世界的腺病毒疫苗（嬌生、牛津、史普尼克疫苗）之原理|url=https://pansci.asia/archives/311975|accessdate=2021-04-07|work=泛科學|date=2021-03-04|archivedate=2021-03-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304042737/https://pansci.asia/archives/311975|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包含[[严重急性呼吸系统综合征冠状病毒2|SARS-CoV-2]]的全长结构表面糖蛋白（[[冠狀病毒刺突蛋白|S蛋白]]）的腺病毒载体疫苗<ref>{{cite journal|title=Severe acute respiratory syndrome-coronavirus-2 spike (S) protein based vaccine candidates: State of the art and future prospects|journal=Reviews in Medical Virology|issue=n/a|doi=10.1002/rmv.2183|year=2020|volume=n/a|pages=e2183|pmc=7646037|pmid=33594794|display-authors=6|vauthors=Arashkia A, Jalilvand S, Mohajel N, Afchangi A, Azadmanesh K, Salehi-Vaziri M, Fazlalipour M, Pouriayevali MH, Jalali T, Mousavi Nasab SD, Roohvand F, Shoja}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Native-like SARS-CoV-2 spike glycoprotein expressed by ChAdOx1 nCoV-19/AZD1222 vaccine|last19=Green|last14=Krebs|first14=A. S.|last15=Dejnirattisai|first15=W.|last16=Mongkolsapaya|first16=J.|last17=Supasa|first17=P.|last18=Screaton|first18=G. R.|first19=C. M.|last13=Morris|last20=Lambe|first20=T.|last21=Zhang|first21=P.|last22=Gilbert|first22=S. C.|last23=Crispin|first23=M.|journal=bioRxiv : The Preprint Server for Biology|pages=2021.01.15.426463|doi=10.1101/2021.01.15.426463|first13=S.|first12=S.|year=2021|first5=M.|pmc=7836103|last1=Watanabe|first1=Y.|last2=Mendonça|first2=L.|last3=Allen|first3=E. R.|last4=Howe|first4=A.|last5=Lee|last6=Allen|last12=Belij-Rammerstorfer|first6=J. D.|last7=Chawla|first7=H.|last8=Pulido|first8=D.|last9=Donnellan|first9=F.|last10=Davies|first10=H.|last11=Ulaszewska|first11=M.|pmid=33501433}}</ref><ref name="新冠疫苗专题报告">{{cite news|title=新冠疫苗专题报告：临床数据亮眼，全球开始签订采购意向|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/stockzmt/2020-09-30/doc-iivhuipp7416062.shtml|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=新浪财经|date=2020-09-30}}</ref>。疫苗接种后，如果之后出现人感染，则会促使免疫系统通过[[抗体|抗体]]和[[T细胞|T细胞]]来攻击冠状病毒<ref name="AstraZeneca_PR">{{cite press release|title=AZD1222 vaccine met primary efficacy endpoint in preventing COVID-19|work=Press Release|publisher=[[阿斯利康|阿斯利康]]|date=2020-11-23|url=https://www.astrazeneca.com/media-centre/press-releases/2020/azd1222hlr.html|accessdate=2021-01-05|archivedate=2021-02-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208133623/https://www.astrazeneca.com/media-centre/press-releases/2020/azd1222hlr.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==历史==
===研发===
該疫苗源於牛津大學[[詹納研究所|詹納研究所]]和Vaccitech之間的合作，Vaccitech是一家從該大學分離出來的私人公司，資金來自牛津科學創新、谷歌風險投資和紅杉資本等企業。疫苗的開發團隊由[[莎拉·吉爾伯特_(疫苗學家)|莎拉·吉爾伯特]]與[[阿德里安·希爾|阿德里安·希爾]]領導，組員有[[安德魯·波拉德|安德魯·波拉德]]、[[特蕾莎·蘭貝|特蕾莎·蘭貝]]、[[桑迪·道格拉斯|桑迪·道格拉斯]]和[[凱瑟琳·格林|凱瑟琳·格林]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://covid19vaccinetrial.co.uk/ |title=The Oxford Vaccine Centre’s COVID-19 vaccine trial |access-date=2021-09-10 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128201533/https://covid19vaccinetrial.co.uk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年2月，牛津大學詹納研究所同意與位於意大利[[波梅齊亞|波梅齊亞]]的疫苗製造商Advent Srl合作開發2019冠狀病毒疫苗，並生產首批1,000劑候選疫苗用於臨床試驗<ref>{{cite web|title=Oxford team to begin novel coronavirus vaccine research|url=https://www.ox.ac.uk/news/2020-02-07-oxford-team-begin-novel-coronavirus-vaccine-research|accessdate=2021-01-02|publisher=University of Oxford|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128201553/https://www.ox.ac.uk/news/2020-02-07-oxford-team-begin-novel-coronavirus-vaccine-research|archivedate=2020-11-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。牛津大學最初打算將生產和銷售權利捐贈給任何想以成本價出售該款疫苗的製藥商，但在2020年3月<ref>{{cite news|title=Covid Vaccine Front-Runner Is Months Ahead of Her Competition|date=2020-07-15|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2020-07-15/oxford-s-covid-19-vaccine-is-the-coronavirus-front-runner|work=Bloomberg Businessweek|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-04-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418054829/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2020-07-15/oxford-s-covid-19-vaccine-is-the-coronavirus-front-runner|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bill Gates, the Virus and the Quest to Vaccinate the World|date=2020-11-23|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/23/world/bill-gates-vaccine-coronavirus.html|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-04-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420153808/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/23/world/bill-gates-vaccine-coronavirus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為研發計劃提供資助的[[盖茨基金会|盖茨基金会]]要求牛津大學尋找一家大型製藥公司合伙，使研發出來的疫苗可以更快生產及上市，故该大学於2020年5月放弃了先前向任何制药公司捐赠权利的承诺<ref>{{cite web|title=They Pledged to Donate Rights to Their COVID Vaccine, Then Sold Them to Pharma|url=https://khn.org/news/rather-than-give-away-its-covid-vaccine-oxford-makes-a-deal-with-drugmaker/|accessdate=2021-01-28|work=Kaiser Health News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207230036/https://khn.org/news/rather-than-give-away-its-covid-vaccine-oxford-makes-a-deal-with-drugmaker/|archivedate=2021-02-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。英国政府鼓励牛津大学与英國[[阿斯利康製藥|阿斯利康製藥]]合作，而不是与美国[[默克公司|默克公司]]合作。据《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》的匿名消息来源称，英國政府担心牛津大學的疫苗如果在美国生产，要運到英國使用可能會遇到阻礙，牛津大学和衍生公司的财务考慮也可能是能否達成合作的因素之一<ref>{{cite web|title=Oxford Developed Covid Vaccine, Then Scholars Clashed Over Money|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/oxford-developed-covid-vaccine-then-scholars-clashed-over-money-11603300412|accessdate=2021-04-01|date=2020-10-21|work=The Wall Street Journal|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207122223/https://www.wsj.com/articles/oxford-developed-covid-vaccine-then-scholars-clashed-over-money-11603300412|archivedate=2021-02-07|dead-url=no|vauthors=Strasburg J, Woo S}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Oxford Developed Covid Vaccine, Then Scholars Clashed Over Money|url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/oxford-developed-covid-vaccine-then-scholars-clashed-over-money/ar-BB1agoI3|accessdate=2021-04-01|work=www.msn.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127221529/https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/oxford-developed-covid-vaccine-then-scholars-clashed-over-money/ar-BB1agoI3|archivedate=2021-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。牛津大學詹納研究所總監Adrian Hill曾經向《華爾街日報》透露未能與北美地區製藥公司達成合作協議的原因，是當地藥企一般要求有獨家製作權才會投資生產疫苗，但他不認同製藥公司在全球疫情大爆發時要求有獨家專利並從疫情中謀取暴利，所以他的團隊才會與不同公司商議合作<ref name="牛津疫苗為何如此快進入臨床階段">{{cite news|title=牛津疫苗為何如此快進入臨床階段？|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5/|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=立場新聞|date=2020-04-28|archivedate=2020-05-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516034018/https://www.thestandnews.com/%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於阿斯利康製藥承諾以成本價一劑幾美金出售共同研發的疫苗<ref name="阿斯利康成本價發售">{{cite news|title=牛津或10月推出 阿斯利康：成本價發售|url=https://inews.hket.com/article/2713210/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E6%88%9610%E6%9C%88%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%20%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%83%B9%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE|accessdate=2021-04-04|work=香港經濟日報|date=2020-08-03|archivedate=2021-04-04|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210404103356/https://inews.hket.com/article/2713210/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E7%89%9B%E6%B4%A5%E6%88%9610%E6%9C%88%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%20%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%83%B9%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE|dead-url=no}}</ref>，所以牛津大學最後便與這家英國製藥公司展開合作。

牛津大學詹納研究所總監Adrian Hill表示，詹納研究所對黑猩猩腺病毒載體的研究已有20年，曾經進行超過70次臨床試驗，最初是期望可開發出[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]疫苗，可惜成效並不顯著，研究所在2014年修改黑猩猩腺病毒載體用於預防[[中東呼吸綜合症|中東呼吸綜合症]]，在英國的臨床測試證實安全後，便在2019年12月在沙特阿拉伯展開試驗。當2020年初傳出科學家在中國[[武漢|武漢]]辨識出一種[[嚴重急性呼吸道症候群冠狀病毒2型|新病毒]]基因後，研究所便立即嘗試以同一種黑猩猩腺病毒載體測試是否能夠用於這種新病毒<ref name="牛津疫苗為何如此快進入臨床階段"/>。[[國家衛生院_(美國)|美國國家健康研究所]]在3月向6隻[[獼猴|獼猴]]注射牛津大學研發的黑猩猩腺病毒載體疫苗，再讓牠們曝露於大量有[[嚴重急性呼吸道症候群冠狀病毒2型|嚴重急性呼吸道症候群冠狀病毒2型]]的環境下，接種了疫苗的6隻獼猴在28日後仍然健康，而其他沒有接種疫苗的獼猴則出現病徵。牛津大學在2020年4月表示臨床試驗需要有6,000人參與，首階段臨床試驗將有約1,000人參與，5月將會開始第二及三階段，包括另外的5,000人<ref name="牛津疫苗為何如此快進入臨床階段"/>。

2020年6月，[[美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所|美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所]]确认，由牛津大学和阿斯利康研发的疫苗的第三阶段临床试验将于2020年7月开始<ref>{{cite web|title=Final testing stage for potential coronavirus vaccine set to begin in July|url=https://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/501999-final-testing-stage-for-coronavirus-vaccine-could-begin-in-july-report|accessdate=2020-06-11|date=2020-06-10|work=The Hill|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110124831/https://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/501999-final-testing-stage-for-coronavirus-vaccine-could-begin-in-july-report|archivedate=2021-01-10|dead-url=no|vauthors=Coleman J}}</ref>。

===临床试验===
2020年7月，阿斯利康与[[昆泰|昆泰]]合作，加速在美国临床试验的进度<ref>{{cite web|title=AZN, IQV Team Up To Accelerate COVID-19 Vaccine Work, RIGL's ITP Drug Repurposed, IMV On Watch|url=https://www.nasdaq.com/articles/azn-iqv-team-up-to-accelerate-covid-19-vaccine-work-rigls-itp-drug-repurposed-imv-on-watch|accessdate=2020-07-15|work=RTTNews|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126192951/https://www.nasdaq.com/articles/azn-iqv-team-up-to-accelerate-covid-19-vaccine-work-rigls-itp-drug-repurposed-imv-on-watch|archivedate=2021-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年8月31日，阿斯利康宣布已开始招募成年人加入由美国资助的，由30,000名受试者组成的后期研究<ref>{{cite web|title=Phase 3 Clinical Testing in the US of AstraZeneca COVID-19 Vaccine Candidate Begins|url=https://www.nih.gov/news-events/news-releases/phase-3-clinical-testing-us-astrazeneca-covid-19-vaccine-candidate-begins|accessdate=2020-09-01|date=2020-08-30|work=National Institutes of Health (NIH)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402102203/https://www.nih.gov/news-events/news-releases/phase-3-clinical-testing-us-astrazeneca-covid-19-vaccine-candidate-begins|archivedate=2021-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年9月8日，阿斯利康表示，由于英国一项研究中的一名接受測試者出现[[贯穿性脊髓炎|贯穿性脊髓炎]]，该公司暂停了疫苗的临床试验<ref name="NYTimes Vaccine">{{cite news|author1=Carl Zimmer|author2=Jonathan Corum|author3=Sui-Lee Wee|title=Coronavirus Vaccine Tracker|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/science/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker.html|accessdate=2021-01-25|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2021-01-25|archivedate=2020-12-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224200821/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/science/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月13日，英国独立调查委员会和监管机构认可该款疫苗的安全性，阿斯利康和牛津大学在英国恢复了临床试验<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Loftus P|date=13 September 2020|title=AstraZeneca Covid-19 Vaccine Trials Resume in U.K.|work=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/astrazeneca-covid-19-vaccine-trials-resume-in-the-u-k-11599922981|accessdate=2020-09-13|archivedate=2021-02-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220022004/https://www.wsj.com/articles/astrazeneca-covid-19-vaccine-trials-resume-in-the-u-k-11599922981|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有专家對阿斯利康公司的試驗提出批评，認為该公司沒有提供在英國的两名参与者出現严重神经系统疾病的详细信息<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Grady D, Wu KJ, LaFraniere S|date=2020-09-19|title=AstraZeneca, Under Fire for Vaccine Safety, Releases Trial Blueprints|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/19/health/astrazeneca-vaccine-safety-blueprints.html|accessdate=2020-09-22|issn=0362-4331|archivedate=2021-03-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318233334/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/19/health/astrazeneca-vaccine-safety-blueprints.html/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后在巴西、南非、印度和日本获准恢复试验<ref>{{cite web|title=COVID-19 vaccine AZD1222 clinical trial resumed in Japan, follows restart of trials in the UK, Brazil, South Africa and India|url=https://www.astrazeneca.com/content/astraz/media-centre/press-releases/2020/covid-19-vaccine-azd1222-clinical-trial-resumed-in-japan-follows-restart-of-trials-in-the-uk-brazil-south-africa-and-india.html|accessdate=2020-10-11|work=阿斯利康|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219230135/https://www.astrazeneca.com/content/astraz/media-centre/press-releases/2020/covid-19-vaccine-azd1222-clinical-trial-resumed-in-japan-follows-restart-of-trials-in-the-uk-brazil-south-africa-and-india.html|archivedate=2020-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，10月23日該疫苗在美國也恢复臨床試驗<ref>{{cite news|title=阿斯利康在美国获批恢复武漢疫苗临床试验|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-10/24/c_1126651871.htm|accessdate=2020-10-24|archivedate=2020-11-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112214239/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-10/24/c_1126651871.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月23日，牛津大学和阿斯利康發表该疫苗第三期临床试验的中期報告<ref name="AstraZeneca_PR" /><ref>{{cite press release|title=Oxford University breakthrough on global COVID-19 vaccine|publisher=University of Oxford|date=23 November 2020|url=https://www.ox.ac.uk/news/2020-11-23-oxford-university-breakthrough-global-covid-19-vaccine|accessdate=2021-01-12|archivedate=2021-03-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323191545/https://www.ox.ac.uk/news/2020-11-23-oxford-university-breakthrough-global-covid-19-vaccine|dead-url=no}}</ref>，顯示该款疫苗的平均有效率为70%，首次注射一半劑量加第二次注射全劑量的有效率90%，兩次都注射全劑量的有效率62%，雖然該臨床試驗報告反映了所收集的測試數據，但首次注射半劑量比注射完整劑量效果更好的試驗结果，卻受到一些質疑<ref name="Nature1">{{cite journal|title=Why Oxford's positive COVID vaccine results are puzzling scientists|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-03326-w|date=23 November 2020|journal=Nature|accessdate=2021-04-01|issue=7836|volume=588|pages=16–18|bibcode=2020Natur.588...16C|pmid=33230278|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125231906/https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-03326-w|archivedate=2020-11-25|vauthors=Callaway E|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=2020-11-27|title=Oxford/AstraZeneca Covid vaccine 'dose error' explained|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-55086927|accessdate=2020-11-27|archivedate=2021-04-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419093025/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-55086927|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Robbins R, Mueller B|date=2020-11-25|title=After Admitting Mistake, AstraZeneca Faces Difficult Questions About Its Vaccine|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/25/business/coronavirus-vaccine-astrazeneca-oxford.html|accessdate=2020-11-27|issn=0362-4331|archivedate=2021-03-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327063015/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/25/business/coronavirus-vaccine-astrazeneca-oxford.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=科興疫苗有效率低惹疑慮 理性爭論與急切抗疫應當並行|url=https://www.hk01.com/周報/576751/科興疫苗有效率低惹疑慮-理性爭論與急切抗疫應當並行|accessdate=2021-04-29|date=2021-01-20|last=葉德豪|first=藺思含|work=香港01|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210708211114/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/576751/%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E4%BD%8E%E6%83%B9%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE-%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E7%88%AD%E8%AB%96%E8%88%87%E6%80%A5%E5%88%87%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E6%87%89%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%A6%E8%A1%8C|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿斯利康回应称，在英国临床试验中，发现一些受试者在接種半剂量疫苗的耐受性更好，促使研發團隊“探索这种给药方案的有效性”。之后阿斯利康与[[美国食品药品管理局|美国食品药品管理局]]进行讨论，修改临床试验的设计方案，增加疫苗劑量的測試選項，并评估两种不同剂量方案的潜力<ref>{{cite news|author1=钱童心|title=阿斯利康回应半剂量方案可显著提升疫苗有效性|url=https://www.yicai.com/news/100850300.html|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=第一财经|date=2020-11-24|archivedate=2020-11-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130062445/https://www.yicai.com/news/100850300.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据英国《[[卫报|卫报]]》报道，在臨床試驗中對一批有2700名的志愿者进行注射时，因為操作人员發生失误，在第一轮接種只注射了一半的剂量，第二轮才使用完整剂量<ref>{{cite news|author1=刘皓然|title=疫苗试验数据和有效性遭质疑，阿斯利康拟启动新试验|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/11-28/9349449.shtml|accessdate=2021-03-26|work=环球网|date=2020-11-28|archivedate=2020-11-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128135622/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2020/11-28/9349449.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，卻意外地發現有更佳的效果。11月26日，阿斯利康首席执行官帕斯卡尔·索里奥特表示，阿斯利康疫苗将进行另一项实验，评估注射較低剂量的疫苗效果<ref>{{cite news|title=阿斯利康CEO：或进行全球新试验，评估武漢疫苗低剂量效果|url=http://www.sznews.com/news/content/2020-11/27/content_23758129.htm?prolongation=1|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=澎湃新闻|date=2020-11-27}}</ref>。

牛津大學與阿斯利康於2020年12月8日在醫學期刊《[[柳葉刀|柳葉刀]]》刊登疫苗的第三阶段臨床试验的中期報告，澄清了这些資訊<ref name="Voysey">{{Cite journal|title=Safety and efficacy of the ChAdOx1 nCoV-19 vaccine (AZD1222) against SARS-CoV-2: an interim analysis of four randomised controlled trials in Brazil, South Africa, and the UK|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0140673620326611|last=Voysey|first=Merryn|last2=Clemens|first2=Sue Ann Costa|date=2021-01-XX|journal=The Lancet|issue=10269|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(20)32661-1|volume=397|pages=99–111|language=en|pmc=PMC7723445|pmid=33306989|last3=Madhi|first3=Shabir A|last4=Weckx|first4=Lily Y|last5=Folegatti|first5=Pedro M|last6=Aley|first6=Parvinder K|last7=Angus|first7=Brian|last8=Baillie|first8=Vicky L|last9=Barnabas|first9=Shaun L|access-date=2021-04-29|archive-date=2021-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621210309/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0140673620326611|dead-url=no}}</ref>，研究團隊再於2021年2月19日在《柳葉刀》發表接種疫苗的時間管理及分析，顯示接種第一劑疫苗後的第22天注射第二劑的有效率为76%，如將接種第二剂的時間延遲至第一剂的第12周或更久，有效率可提高至81.3%<ref name="Voysev_Feb21">{{Cite journal|title=Single-dose administration and the influence of the timing of the booster dose on immunogenicity and efficacy of ChAdOx1 nCoV-19 (AZD1222) vaccine: a pooled analysis of four randomised trials|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(21)00432-3/abstract|last=Voysey|first=Merryn|last2=Clemens|first2=Sue Ann Costa|date=2021-03-06|journal=The Lancet|issue=10277|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(21)00432-3|volume=397|pages=881–891|language=en|issn=0140-6736|pmid=33617777|last3=Madhi|first3=Shabir A.|last4=Weckx|first4=Lily Y.|last5=Folegatti|first5=Pedro M.|last6=Aley|first6=Parvinder K.|last7=Angus|first7=Brian|last8=Baillie|first8=Vicky L.|last9=Barnabas|first9=Shaun L.}}</ref>。

2021年3月22日，阿斯利康公司公布美国临床试验结果，预防感染的有效率为79%，预防严重疾病和住院的有效率为100%<ref>{{cite news|title=AZD1222 US Phase III trial met primary efficacy endpoint in preventing COVID-19 at interim analysis|url=https://www.astrazeneca.com/content/astraz/media-centre/press-releases/2021/astrazeneca-us-vaccine-trial-met-primary-endpoint.html|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=阿斯利康|date=2021-03-22|language=en|archivedate=2021-04-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411084820/https://www.astrazeneca.com/content/astraz/media-centre/press-releases/2021/astrazeneca-us-vaccine-trial-met-primary-endpoint.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国国家卫生研究院发表声明称，该疫苗在美国和南美地区开展的临床试验结果显示，接种疫苗的志愿者出现血栓的风险没有增加<ref>{{cite news|author1=谭晶晶|title=美国家卫生研究院：阿斯利康疫苗临床试验参与者血栓风险未增加|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2021-03/23/c_1127246301.htm|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=新华社|date=2021-03-23}}</ref>。2021年3月23日，[[美国国立卫生研究院|美国国立卫生研究院]]发表声明称[[美国国家过敏和传染病研究所|美国国家过敏和传染病研究所]]下属的一个{{le|数据安全监测委员会|Data monitoring committee}}（DSMB）在22日晚间公布调查报告，对阿斯利康疫苗公布的初步临床试验数据表示担忧，质疑其提供的数据不完整，要求重新审查。聲明中称：“我們敦促該公司（阿斯利康）與DSMB一起審查功效數據，並確保盡快公佈最準確，最新的功效數據。”並補充說，DSMB已將其擔憂告知了阿斯利康。路透社认为，DSMB反饋的含義是，阿斯利康在一部分患者中可能誇大了疫苗的功效。德國[[圖賓根大學|圖賓根大學]]醫学院教授彼得·克雷姆斯納则表示：“這对于DMSB来说確實是一種非同尋常的行為。關於這種疫苗的負面報導沒有停止，儘管我的評估是它具有良好的耐受性和安全性，但明顯不如兩種mRNA疫苗（[[輝瑞疫苗|輝瑞疫苗]]及[[莫德納疫苗|莫德納疫苗]]）有效。”<ref>{{cite web|title=U.S. health body questions AstraZeneca's COVID-19 vaccine trial data|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-astrazeneca-u-s/astrazeneca-may-have-included-outdated-info-from-u-s-vaccine-trial-niaid-idUSKBN2BF0CV|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=路透社|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Experts comment on U.S. questioning of AstraZeneca trial data|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-astrazeneca-usa-qu/experts-comment-on-u-s-questioning-of-astrazeneca-trial-data-idUSKBN2BF1CJ|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=路透社|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331221234/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-astrazeneca-usa-qu/experts-comment-on-u-s-questioning-of-astrazeneca-trial-data-idUSKBN2BF1CJ|archivedate=2021-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>世界卫生组织则在一份声明中表示：“根据我们的理解，NIAID的担忧似乎与疫苗有效性的数据有关，而不是安全性。我们既没有看到来自美国AZ临床试验的数据，也没有看到有关NIAID担忧的细节。”<ref>{{cite web|title=Concerns about AstraZeneca vaccine data don't seem to be related to safety, WHO says|url=https://cnnphilippines.com/world/2021/3/24/astrazeneca-vaccine-data-not-related-safety-WHO.html|accessdate=2021-03-23|work=CNN|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324213942/https://cnnphilippines.com/world/2021/3/24/astrazeneca-vaccine-data-not-related-safety-WHO.html|archivedate=2021-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===2021年的研究===
2021年2月，牛津大学和阿斯利康公司指出，将开始推进使疫苗适应[[严重急性呼吸综合征冠状病毒2变种|冠状病毒新变种]]的研究工作<ref>{{cite web|title=AstraZeneca races to adapt Covid vaccine as South Africa suspends rollout|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/08/astrazeneca-races-to-adapt-covid-vaccine-as-south-africa-halts-rollout.html|accessdate=2021-02-08|date=2021-02-08|publisher=CNBC|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302154710/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/08/astrazeneca-races-to-adapt-covid-vaccine-as-south-africa-halts-rollout.html|archivedate=2021-03-02|dead-url=no|vauthors=Ellyatt H}}</ref>，并期望经过改良的疫苗将在几个月内流入市场<ref name="Triggle-20210208">{{cite news|vauthors=Triggle N|date=2021-02-08|accessdate=2021-02-09|title=Covid: Are fears over Oxford-AstraZeneca jab justified?|publisher=BBC|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-55921815|archivedate=2021-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301083132/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-55921815|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新型冠状病毒從中國蔓延到全球後已出現多個變種<ref name="COVID-19變種">{{Cite web|title=新冠肺炎︱美國研究：南非變種對疫苗抵抗能力高逾20倍|url=https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/599981/新冠肺炎-美國研究-南非變種對疫苗抵抗能力高逾20倍|accessdate=2021-04-29|date=2021-03-16|last=歐敬洛|work=香港01|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://archive.today/20210417100048/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/599981/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E5%B0%8D%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%97%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E9%AB%98%E9%80%BE20%E5%80%8D|dead-url=no}}</ref>，可能削弱應用或研發中的疫苗對抗病毒的有效性<ref name="變種削疫苗效用">{{cite news|title=「變上變」削疫苗效用|url=https://www.wenweipo.com/s/202104/01/AP6064ddffe4b04e1918ce6d01.html|accessdate=2021-04-17|work=文匯報|date=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-04-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417103439/https://www.wenweipo.com/s/202104/01/AP6064ddffe4b04e1918ce6d01.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中一個研究的关键领域是由E484K突变的病毒是否会影响免疫反应，并可能影响疫苗的有效性<ref name="BMJ2021-372n359">{{Cite journal|title=Covid-19: The E484K mutation and the risks it poses|url=https://www.bmj.com/lookup/doi/10.1136/bmj.n359|last=Wise|first=Jacqui|date=2021-02-05|journal=BMJ|doi=10.1136/bmj.n359|pages=n359|language=en|issn=1756-1833}}</ref>。E484K突变存在于南非变种病毒（B.1.351）和巴西变种病毒（B.1.1.28）中，有少数病例在原始的SARS-CoV-2病毒和英国变种病毒（[[VOC-202012/01|B.1.1.7]]）中也发现了突变<ref name="BMJ2021-372n359"/>。阿斯利康疫苗可以應對巴西變種病毒，但對南非變種病毒的保護率只有10%<ref name="變種削疫苗效用"/>。

===苏格兰的研究===
在[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]境内的各高校进行了一项针对540万人的全国前瞻性队列研究，研究了第一剂量的[[辉瑞疫苗|辉瑞疫苗]]和牛津–阿斯利康疫苗对苏格兰住院病人的有效性。在2020年12月8日至2021年2月15日期间的研究中，有1,137,775例患者接种了疫苗，其中490,000例接受了牛津-阿斯利康疫苗的接种。牛津-阿斯利康疫苗的第一剂在疫苗接种后的28至34天，其有效率达到94%。两种疫苗组合的结果均显示疫苗對预防住院的效果，当分析限制在80岁以上的人群时（81%），该效果是可比的。65岁以上的大多数患者都接种了牛津-阿斯利康疫苗。截至2021年2月22日，该研究尚未经过[[同行评审|同行评审]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Covid-19: First doses of vaccines in Scotland led to a substantial fall in hospital admissions|url=https://www.bmj.com/content/372/bmj.n523|accessdate=2021-02-25|work=the BMJ|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210408130549/https://www.bmj.com/content/372/bmj.n523|archivedate=2021-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=scotland first vaccine data preprint|url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/files/atoms/files/scotland_firstvaccinedata_preprint.pdf|accessdate=2021-02-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328005423/https://www.ed.ac.uk/files/atoms/files/scotland_firstvaccinedata_preprint.pdf|archivedate=2021-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===韓國的高齡人群實際環境調查報告===
[[韓國政府|韓國政府]]在2021年4月26日發表調查報告顯示對於75歲以上的高齡人群，阿斯利康疫苗的預防感染有效率是100%<ref name="韓國高齡保護率達百分百">{{cite news|title=南韓75歲以上接種阿斯利康疫苗後保護率達百分百|url=https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=432527|accessdate=2021-04-27|work=Now新聞|date=2021-04-26}}</ref>，而[[輝瑞疫苗|輝瑞疫苗]]的有效率是93.2%，反映阿斯利康疫苗及輝瑞疫苗對高齡人群的保護率都表現理想。韓國政府從2021年2月26日至4月21日對已接種第一劑疫苗的751,687人進行調查發現，在完成第一劑疫苗14日後，接種阿斯利康疫苗的人群沒有人受到感染<ref name="韓國75歲100%">{{cite news|title=韩政府：高龄接种两周后阿斯利康疫苗保护率100%|url=https://m-cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210426004000881|agency=韩联社|date=2021-04-26|accessdate=2021-04-27|archive-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429192814/https://m-cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210426004000881|dead-url=no}}</ref>，輝瑞疫苗則有兩人受到感染。同期沒有接種疫苗的3,136,142名75歲以上的高齡人群則有906人染病，每10萬人就有28.9宗受感染個案，受感染的機會即使與接種輝瑞疫苗的人群相比也高14倍。[[韓國國務總理|韓國國務總理]]洪楠基在4月26日表示韓國目前正在使用的阿斯利康疫苗及輝瑞疫苗在安全性及有效率都得到國際公認<ref name="韓國75歲100%" />。

===巴林的真實環境保護力研究===
2021年8月28日，[[巴林|巴林]]與美國[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]對該國實施大規模疫苗接種計劃後進行的研究發現，阿斯利康疫苗在巴林真實環境下對預防重症及死亡的保護效果最佳<ref name="巴林研究：AZ預防死亡優於輝瑞">{{cite news |title=巴林研究：AZ預防住院和死亡優於輝瑞 中國國藥最差 |url=https://udn.com/news/story/121707/5707169 |accessdate=2021-09-01 |work=聯合報 |date=2021-08-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210901110903/https://udn.com/news/story/121707/5707169 |archivedate=2021-09-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。巴林自2020年12月起為該國約150萬人口分別接種中國[[眾愛可維2019冠狀病毒病疫苗|國藥眾愛可維]]、俄羅斯[[衛星五號|衛星五號]]（Sputnik-V）、美國輝瑞疫苗及印度生產的阿斯利康疫苗（Covishield），至2021年8月全國已有66%的人口完成接種，雖然這些疫苗都可減少重症，但接種中國國藥疫苗染疫後的死亡率是0.46%，高於輝瑞疫苗的0.15%及死亡率最低的阿斯利康疫苗0.03%，而俄羅斯衛星五號則介於中國國藥與美國輝瑞之間，在減少住院方面，阿斯利康疫苗1.52%的住院率不但低於中國國藥及衛星五號，也優於輝瑞疫苗的1.99%<ref name="國藥疫苗預防住院及死亡不及輝瑞">{{cite news |title=研究指國藥疫苗預防感染、住院及死亡不及輝瑞 |url=https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2896629/研究指國藥疫苗預防感染、住院及死亡不及輝瑞 |accessdate=2021-09-01 |work=信報 |date=2021-08-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210901110949/https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2896629/%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%8B%E8%97%A5%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8F%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%8A%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E |archivedate=2021-09-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，即使Delta變異病毒株出現後，保護力的差異也沒有改變，由於中國國藥疫苗對預防重症及死亡的表現最差<ref name="巴林研究：AZ預防死亡優於輝瑞"/>，巴林政府於2021年5月決定為完成接種兩劑國藥疫苗的國民注射輝瑞或其他疫苗作為加強劑<ref name="國藥疫苗預防住院及死亡不及輝瑞"/>。

==生产、获批和供应==
该疫苗可在冰箱冷藏室储存，每剂价格约3到4美元（3英鎊）<ref name="牛津疫苗研發成功" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Why the AstraZeneca-Oxford Covid-19 vaccine is different|url=https://www.vox.com/21590994/oxford-vaccine-results-covid-19-astrazeneca-trial-pfizer-moderna|accessdate=2021-04-29|date=2020-11-23|last=Belluz|first=Julia|work=Vox|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129080053/https://www.vox.com/21590994/oxford-vaccine-results-covid-19-astrazeneca-trial-pfizer-moderna|archivedate=2021-01-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年12月17日，比利时官员在Twitter上透露，欧盟将为每剂疫苗支付1.78欧元（2.16美元），《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》暗示较低的价格可能与包括由欧盟主导的疫苗生产基础设施投资在内的因素有关。<ref>{{cite news|title=A European Official Reveals a Secret: The U.S. Is Paying More for Coronavirus Vaccines|vauthors=Stevis-Gridneff M, Sanger-Katz M, Weiland N|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2020-12-18|accessdate=2020-12-19|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/18/upshot/coronavirus-vaccines-prices-europe-united-states.html|archivedate=2021-03-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328072519/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/18/upshot/coronavirus-vaccines-prices-europe-united-states.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

截至2021年3月，该款疫苗已在全球多个地点生产<ref name="BBCwheremade">{{cite news|title=Where is the Oxford-AstraZeneca vaccine made?|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/56483766|accessdate=2021-03-27|work=BBC News|archivedate=2021-04-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420212637/https://www.bbc.com/news/56483766|dead-url=no}}</ref>，阿斯利康表示已在全球15个国家和地区的25个城市设立生产厂<ref name="AX15-25claim">{{cite web|title=Delivering COVID-19 vaccine part 2|url=https://www.astrazeneca.com/what-science-can-do/topics/technologies/pushing-boundaries-to-deliver-covid-19-vaccine-accross-the-globe.html|accessdate=2021-03-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331192023/https://www.astrazeneca.com/what-science-can-do/topics/technologies/pushing-boundaries-to-deliver-covid-19-vaccine-accross-the-globe.html|archivedate=2021-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括英國、比利時、荷蘭<ref name="歐盟要求阿斯利康英國廠增產"/>、意大利、印度<ref name="印度代產阿斯利康疫苗"/>、韓國<ref name="牛津疫苗列入世衛使用清單"/>、日本<ref name="日本藥廠生產1.2億劑"/>、澳洲等。截至2021年6月19日，阿斯利康已在全球130个国家和地区投入使用<ref>{{Cite news|title=Coronavirus: Setback for EU in legal fight with AstraZeneca|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-57531064|newspaper=BBC News|date=2021-06-18|accessdate=2021-06-19|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210626160215/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-57531064|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

据阿斯利康负责运营和IT的副总裁Pam Cheng称，至2020年底，该公司将在全球范围内供应约2亿剂疫苗。一旦产能提高，每月产能将达到1亿至2亿剂<ref name=Nature1 />。

===获批和供应时间线===
{{seealso|2019冠状病毒病疫苗授权列表}}
2020年6月，阿斯利康除了向英国[[國民保健署|国民医疗服务体系]]推出的[[英國2019冠狀病毒病疫苗接種計劃|疫苗接种计划]]提供1亿剂疫苗外，该公司也与美国{{le|Emergent BioSolutions|Emergent BioSolutions}}公司签署了一份8700万美元的协议，专门为美国市场生产该疫苗。此次交易是特朗普政府提出的“[[曲速行動|曲速行動]]”的一部分，该倡议旨在在2020年底之前开发并快速扩大目标疫苗的生产规模，以供[[美國2019冠狀病毒病疫苗接種計劃|美國2019冠狀病毒病疫苗接種計劃]]使用<ref>{{cite web|title=AstraZeneca, Emergent BioSolutions sign $87M deal to produce U.S. supply of COVID-19 vaccine|url=https://www.fiercepharma.com/manufacturing/astrazeneca-emergent-biosolutions-sign-87m-deal-to-produce-u-s-supply-covid-vaccine|accessdate=2020-06-12|work=FiercePharma|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218063419/https://www.fiercepharma.com/manufacturing/astrazeneca-emergent-biosolutions-sign-87m-deal-to-produce-u-s-supply-covid-vaccine|archivedate=2021-02-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|Catalent|Catalent}}将承担该疫苗的分装工作<ref>{{cite web|title=AstraZeneca taps Catalent for COVID-19 vaccine finishing, packaging at Italian plant|url=https://www.fiercepharma.com/manufacturing/astrazeneca-taps-catalent-for-covid-19-vaccine-finishing-packaging-at-italian-plant|accessdate=2020-06-16|work=FiercePharma|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303190310/https://www.fiercepharma.com/manufacturing/astrazeneca-taps-catalent-for-covid-19-vaccine-finishing-packaging-at-italian-plant|archivedate=2021-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年6月4日，世界卫生组织发起的[[COVAX|COVAX]]计划通过阿斯利康向中低收入国家首次购买了3亿剂疫苗<ref>{{cite press release|date=2020-06-04|title=Agreements with CEPI and Gavi and the Serum Institute of India will bring vaccine to low and middle-income countries and beyond|url=https://www.astrazeneca.com/media-centre/press-releases/2020/astrazeneca-takes-next-steps-towards-broad-and-equitable-accessto-oxford-universitys-covid-19-vaccine.html|publisher=阿斯利康|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-04-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416001246/https://www.astrazeneca.com/media-centre/press-releases/2020/astrazeneca-takes-next-steps-towards-broad-and-equitable-accessto-oxford-universitys-covid-19-vaccine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，阿斯利康和[[印度血清研究所|印度血清研究所]]达成了许可协议，向包括印度在内的中低收入国家提供10亿剂疫苗<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Rajagopal D|title=AstraZeneca & Serum Institute of India sign licensing deal for 1 billion doses of Oxford vaccine|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/healthcare/biotech/pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-serum-institute-of-india-sign-licensing-deal-for-1-billion-doses-of-oxford-vaccine/articleshow/76202016.cms|work=The Economic Times|date=2020-06-04|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222214731/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/healthcare/biotech/pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-serum-institute-of-india-sign-licensing-deal-for-1-billion-doses-of-oxford-vaccine/articleshow/76202016.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Kumar M|title=Covid-19 vaccine: Serum Institute signs up for 100 million doses of vaccines for India, low and middle-income countries|url=https://www.financialexpress.com/lifestyle/health/covid-19-vaccine-serum-institute-signs-up-for-100-million-doses-of-vaccines-for-india-low-and-middle-income-countries/2047884/|work=The Financial Express|date=2020-08-07|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-02-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202001740/https://www.financialexpress.com/lifestyle/health/covid-19-vaccine-serum-institute-signs-up-for-100-million-doses-of-vaccines-for-india-low-and-middle-income-countries/2047884/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年6月13日，阿斯利康与法国、德国、意大利和荷兰联合组建的包容性疫苗联盟（Inclusive Vaccines Alliance）达成协议，向所有欧盟成员国提供多达4亿剂<ref>{{cite web|title=Covid-19: France, Italy, Germany and Netherlands sign vaccine deal for Europe|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200613-covid-19-france-italy-germany-and-netherlands-sign-vaccine-deal|accessdate=2020-06-15|date=2020-06-13|publisher=France 24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420062337/https://www.france24.com/en/20200613-covid-19-france-italy-germany-and-netherlands-sign-vaccine-deal|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AstraZeneca agrees to supply Europe with 400 mil doses of COVID-19 vaccine|url=https://japantoday.com/category/features/health/update-4-astrazeneca-agrees-to-supply-europe-with-400-mln-doses-of-covid-19-vaccine|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=Japan Today|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110025239/https://japantoday.com/category/features/health/update-4-astrazeneca-agrees-to-supply-europe-with-400-mln-doses-of-covid-19-vaccine|archivedate=2021-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AstraZeneca to supply Europe with Covid-19 vaccine|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/astrazeneca-to-supply-europe-with-covid-19-vaccine-2020-06-15|accessdate=2020-06-15|work=MarketWatch|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126190955/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/astrazeneca-to-supply-europe-with-covid-19-vaccine-2020-06-15|archivedate=2021-01-26|dead-url=no|vauthors=Calatayud A}}</ref>。之后，[[欧盟委员会|欧盟委员会]]代表整个欧盟接手了谈判，并于8月底签署了一项协议<ref>{{cite web|title=What is the dispute between the EU and AstraZeneca over Covid jabs?|url=https://www.itv.com/news/2021-01-26/covid-vaccine-what-is-the-dispute-between-the-eu-and-astrazeneca|accessdate=2021-01-27|date=26 January 2021|work=ITV News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215120812/https://www.itv.com/news/2021-01-26/covid-vaccine-what-is-the-dispute-between-the-eu-and-astrazeneca|archivedate=2021-02-15|dead-url=no|vauthors=Peston R}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Another Fine Mess — The EU's Vaccine (Mis)management|url=https://www.nationalreview.com/2021/02/another-fine-mess-the-eus-vaccine-mismanagement/|accessdate=2021-03-21|date=2021-02-11|work=www.nationalreview.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327202339/https://www.nationalreview.com/2021/02/another-fine-mess-the-eus-vaccine-mismanagement/|archivedate=2021-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=How Europe fell behind on vaccines|url=https://www.politico.eu/article/europe-coronavirus-vaccine-struggle-pfizer-biontech-astrazeneca/|accessdate=2021-03-21|date=2021-01-27|work=www.polico.eu|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418023751/https://www.politico.eu/article/europe-coronavirus-vaccine-struggle-pfizer-biontech-astrazeneca/|archivedate=2021-04-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年8月，阿斯利康同意以12亿美元的价格向美国提供3亿剂疫苗，即每剂疫苗仅4美元。阿斯利康的一位发言人说，这笔资金还包括开发和临床测试<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Roland D|date=2020-05-21|title=U.S. to Invest $1.2 Billion to Secure Potential Coronavirus Vaccine From AstraZeneca, Oxford University|work=The Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-to-invest-1-2-billion-to-secure-potential-coronavirus-vaccine-from-astrazeneca-oxford-university-11590063053|accessdate=2020-08-06|archivedate=2021-04-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404122745/https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-to-invest-1-2-billion-to-secure-potential-coronavirus-vaccine-from-astrazeneca-oxford-university-11590063053|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿斯利康还与墨西哥、阿根廷政府达成了一项技术转让协议，并同意生产至少4亿剂药物，以确保在整个拉丁美洲分发。其疫苗有效成分将在阿根廷生产，之后运送到墨西哥完成分发<ref>{{cite news|title=AstraZeneca set to start making 400 million COVID-19 vaccines for Latam early in 2021|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-latam-vaccine/astrazeneca-set-to-start-making-400-million-covid-19-vaccines-for-latam-early-in-2021-idUSKCN2591Y1|accessdate=2021-01-17|work=Reuters|archivedate=2021-04-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409093902/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-latam-vaccine/astrazeneca-set-to-start-making-400-million-covid-19-vaccines-for-latam-early-in-2021-idUSKCN2591Y1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年8月6日，阿斯利康宣布与[[康泰生物|康泰生物]]签署中国内地市场独家授权合作框架协议，通过技术转让形式实现疫苗在中国内地市场的研发、生产、供应和商业化。根据合作框架协议条款约定，康泰生物作为技术受让方，将确保在2020年底前达到至少1亿剂疫苗的年产能，并在2021年底前将该疫苗设计产能扩大至年产至少2亿剂，以满足中国市场的需求<ref>{{cite news|title=阿斯利康与康泰生物就新冠疫苗达成授权合作|url=https://www.astrazeneca.com.cn/zh/media/press-releases/2020/_1.html|accessdate=2021-04-02|work=阿斯利康中国|date=2020-08-06|language=zh|archivedate=2020-12-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205080956/https://www.astrazeneca.com.cn/zh/media/press-releases/2020/_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，由于2021年3月接连发生的风波，疫苗在中国内地的上市进度可能会受到影响<ref>{{cite news|title=阿斯利康新冠疫苗风波又起 拿下中国代理权的康泰生物还好吗?|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/wm/2021-03-25/doc-ikkntiam8199170.shtml|accessdate=2021-04-02|work=华夏时报|date=2021-03-25|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627224856/https://finance.sina.com.cn/wm/2021-03-25/doc-ikkntiam8199170.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年11月，由康泰生物通过技术转让研制的疫苗被印度尼西亚卫生部门授予紧急使用授权，是中国第二款在境外获批紧急使用的腺病毒载体疫苗<ref>{{cite news |title=400余万支康泰生物新冠疫苗运抵印尼 “深圳苗”首飞海外助力全球抗疫 |url=http://www.sz.gov.cn/szzt2010/yqfk2020/szzxd/content/post_9385570.html |accessdate=2022-03-02 |work=深圳特区报 |date=2021-11-22 |archive-date=2022-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220302170215/http://www.sz.gov.cn/szzt2010/yqfk2020/szzxd/content/post_9385570.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Co.,Ltd |first1=Shenzhen Kangtai Biological Products |title=BioKangtai's adenovirus vector COVID-19 vaccine obtained EUA in Indonesia |url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/biokangtais-adenovirus-vector-covid-19-vaccine-obtained-eua-in-indonesia-301415162.html |accessdate=2022-03-02 |work=www.prnewswire.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321110742/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/biokangtais-adenovirus-vector-covid-19-vaccine-obtained-eua-in-indonesia-301415162.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年9月29日，印度血清研究所、全球免疫联盟与[[盖茨基金会|盖茨基金会]]达成进一步协议，在2021年以每剂不超过3美元向中低收入国家制造和交付另外1亿剂疫苗<ref>{{cite news|title=全球疫苗联盟与印度疫苗生产商合作 承诺为中低收入国家增加提供1亿剂新冠疫苗|url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2020/09/1067982|accessdate=2021-03-28|work=联合国新闻|date=2020-09-29|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303185113/https://news.un.org/zh/story/2020/09/1067982|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，阿斯利康同意向加拿大供应2000万剂疫苗<ref>{{cite web|title=With no successful vaccine candidates yet, Canada signs deal to secure 20M more COVID-19 vaccine doses|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/covid19-briefing-trudeau-tam-1.5738503|accessdate=2021-04-01|date=2020-09-25|publisher=CBC News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320133526/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/covid19-briefing-trudeau-tam-1.5738503|archivedate=2021-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Health Canada begins first authorization review of a COVID-19 vaccine submission|url=https://www.canada.ca/en/health-canada/news/2020/10/health-canada-begins-first-authorization-review-of-a-covid-19-vaccine-submission.html|accessdate=2020-12-30|date=2020-10-02|last=Health Canada|work=gcnws|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330170414/https://www.canada.ca/en/health-canada/news/2020/10/health-canada-begins-first-authorization-review-of-a-covid-19-vaccine-submission.html|archivedate=2021-03-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年10月，瑞士与阿斯利康签署协议，订购530万剂疫苗<ref>{{cite web|title=Swiss sign next vaccine agreement with AstraZeneca|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/swiss-sign-next-vaccine-agreement-with-astrazeneca/46101078|accessdate=2020-10-16|work=SWI swissinfo.ch|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111000919/https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/swiss-sign-next-vaccine-agreement-with-astrazeneca/46101078|archivedate=2021-01-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=COVID-19 vaccine: Swiss federal government signs agreement with AstraZeneca|url=https://www.admin.ch/gov/en/start/documentation/media-releases.msg-id-80732.html|accessdate=2020-10-16|work=admin.ch|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126215134/https://www.admin.ch/gov/en/start/documentation/media-releases.msg-id-80732.html|archivedate=2021-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月5日，孟加拉国政府、印度血清研究所和孟加拉国Beximco Pharma签署三方协议。根据该协议，孟加拉国订购3000万剂疫苗，每次注射价格为4美元<ref name="Dhaka to have 330 vaccination points">{{cite web|title=Dhaka to have 330 vaccination points|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/frontpage/news/dhaka-have-330-vaccination-points-2029465|accessdate=2021-01-25|work=The Daily Star|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128032500/https://www.thedailystar.net/frontpage/news/dhaka-have-330-vaccination-points-2029465|archivedate=2021-01-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月27日，英国政府要求{{le|英国药品和医疗产品监管局|Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency}}（MHRA）评估疫苗的临时供应<ref>{{cite web|title=Government asks regulator to approve supply of Oxford/AstraZeneca vaccine|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/government-asks-regulator-to-approve-supply-of-oxfordastrazeneca-vaccine|accessdate=2020-11-28|date=27 October 2020|publisher=Government of the United Kingdom|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208195258/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/government-asks-regulator-to-approve-supply-of-oxfordastrazeneca-vaccine|archivedate=2021-02-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于2020年12月30日正式批准，作为第二款可在英国接种计划使用的疫苗<ref>{{cite web|title=Oxford University/AstraZeneca vaccine authorised by UK medicines regulator|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/oxford-universityastrazeneca-vaccine-authorised-by-uk-medicines-regulator|accessdate=30 December 2020|date=2020-12-30|publisher=Government of the United Kingdom|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316110433/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/oxford-universityastrazeneca-vaccine-authorised-by-uk-medicines-regulator|archivedate=2021-03-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月，泰国从阿斯利康订购2600万剂疫苗<ref>{{cite news|title=เรื่องน่ารู้ของวัคซีนโควิด-19 ที่ไทยสั่งซื้อ|url=https://www.bbc.com/thai/thailand-55102801|accessdate=2021-01-05|work=BBC ไทย|language=th|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107155404/https://www.bbc.com/thai/thailand-55102801|dead-url=no}}</ref>，可供1300万人接种<ref>{{cite news|title=ทำความรู้จัก ออกซ์ฟอร์ด-แอสทราเซเนกา วัคซีนที่ไทยเลือก|url=https://www.matichon.co.th/article/news_2509958|accessdate=5 January 2021|work=มติชนออนไลน์|date=2021-01-02|language=th|archivedate=2021-04-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418005111/https://www.matichon.co.th/article/news_2509958|dead-url=no}}</ref>，约占泰国人口的20%，第一批产品有望在2021年5月底交付<ref>{{cite news|title=ครม.ไฟเขียวงบซื้อวัคซีนโควิดเพิ่ม35ล้านโดส ฉีดให้คนไทย66ล้าน|url=https://www.posttoday.com/politic/news/642002|accessdate=2021-01-05|work=โพสต์ทูเดย์|language=th|archivedate=2021-01-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128052943/https://www.posttoday.com/politic/news/642002|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=ข่าวดี ไทยเริ่มผลิตวัคซีน 'โควิด-19' ในประเทศ รอบที่ 2 แล้ว|date=2021-01-03|url=https://www.thairath.co.th/news/local/2005712|work=ไทยรัฐออนไลน์|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107072032/https://www.thairath.co.th/news/local/2005712|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=สธ. แจง AstraZeneca เป็นผู้คัดเลือก Siam Bioscience ผลิตวัคซีนราคาทุน ขายถูกสุดในตลาด โต้ธนาธร ไม่ได้แทงม้าตัวเดียว|date=2021-01-19|url=https://thestandard.co/mof-reveals-astrazeneca-choose-siam-bioscience/|work=The Standard|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-02-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207033044/https://thestandard.co/mof-reveals-astrazeneca-choose-siam-bioscience/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。泰国公共卫生部长{{le|阿努汀·查恩维拉库|Anutin Charnvirakul}}表示，每剂疫苗费用为5美元<ref name="hfocus-2020-11-23">{{cite web|title=ข่าวดี! ไทยจองซื้อวัคซีนโควิด-19 แอสตราเซเนกา "ราคาต้นทุน"|url=https://www.hfocus.org/content/2020/11/20493|accessdate=2021-04-01|date=23 November 2020|publisher=hfocus.org|language=th|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123105230/https://www.hfocus.org/content/2020/11/20493|archivedate=2020-11-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>；但泰国阿斯利康公司于2021年1月解释说，每个国家交付的价格取决于生产成本和供应链中的差异，包括制造能力，劳动力和原材料成本<ref>{{cite news|title=วัคซีนโควิด: แอสตร้าเซเนก้าชี้แจงเหตุผลเลือกสยามไบโอไซเอนซ์เป็นผู้ผลิต|date=2021-01-26|url=https://www.bbc.com/thai/thailand-55810764|work=BBC News ไทย|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-02-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210090941/https://www.bbc.com/thai/thailand-55810764|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月，泰国内阁批准了关于再订购3500万剂的进一步谈判<ref>{{cite news|title=โควิด-19: ทำไมรัฐบาลเลือก สยามไบโอไซเอนซ์ ผลิตวัคซีนเพื่อคนไทยและเพื่อนบ้าน|date=2021-01-15|url=https://www.bbc.com/thai/thailand-55672015|work=BBC News ไทย|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-02-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216101357/https://www.bbc.com/thai/thailand-55672015|dead-url=no}}</ref>，泰国药监局亦批准了该疫苗的1年紧急使用期限<ref>{{cite news|title=AstraZeneca vaccine approved, 50,000 doses due in February|date=2021-01-21|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/2054799/astrazeneca-vaccine-approved-50-000-doses-due-in-february|work=Bangkok Post|accessdate=2021-04-01|archive-date=2021-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726010924/https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/2054799/astrazeneca-vaccine-approved-50-000-doses-due-in-february|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=FDA approves AstraZeneca|date=2021-01-22|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/2054847/fda-approves-astrazeneca|work=Bangkok Post|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421043642/https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/2054847/fda-approves-astrazeneca|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[玛哈·哇集拉隆功|玛哈·哇集拉隆功]]持有的暹罗生物科学公司（Siam Bioscience）将获得技术转让<ref>{{cite news|title=นายกฯ สำนึกในพระมหากรุณาธิคุณ ร.10 ทรงให้ "สยามไบโอไซเอนซ์" รองรับวัคซีนโควิด-19|url=https://www.bbc.com/thai/55097716|accessdate=2021-01-05|work=BBC ไทย|date=2020-11-27|language=th|archivedate=2021-03-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306222948/https://www.bbc.com/thai/55097716|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并具有每年制造多达2亿剂剂量向东盟出口的能力<ref>{{cite news|title=35m more shots to be bought in 2021|date=2021-01-05|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/2046003/35m-more-shots-to-be-bought-in-2021|work=Bangkok Post|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421043705/https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/2046003/35m-more-shots-to-be-bought-in-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月，菲律宾同意购买260万剂疫苗<ref>{{cite news|title=Philippines, AstraZeneca Sign Deal for 2.6 Million Doses|date=2020-11-27|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-27/philippines-signs-deal-with-astrazeneca-for-2-6-million-doses|work=Bloomberg|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421043641/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=2b380f70-a25b-11eb-bfcc-a1d2f357f9b2&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMC0xMS0yNy9waGlsaXBwaW5lcy1zaWducy1kZWFsLXdpdGgtYXN0cmF6ZW5lY2EtZm9yLTItNi1taWxsaW9uLWRvc2Vz|dead-url=no}}</ref>，据报道疫苗订购总值约7亿菲律宾比索（折合每剂5.6美元）<ref>{{cite news|title=Over 200 firms to ink deal for more COVID vaccines with gov't, AstraZeneca|date=2021-01-11|url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1382075/over-200-firms-to-ink-covid-vaccine-deal-with-govt-astrazeneca|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-01-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120100221/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1382075/over-200-firms-to-ink-covid-vaccine-deal-with-govt-astrazeneca|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年12月，韩国与阿斯利康签署合同，以确保获得2000万剂疫苗，据称疫苗总值相当于泰国与菲律宾签署的总和<ref>{{cite news|title=Korea signs agreement with AstraZeneca for COVID vaccine|date=2020-11-30|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/tech/2020/12/693_300153.html|work=The Korea Times|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-02-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217113612/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/tech/2020/12/693_300153.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，预计首批装运时间为2021年1月。截至2021年1月，该疫苗仍接受[[韓國疾病管理本部|韓國疾病管理本部]]的审查<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Shin H|date=2020-12-03|title=South Korea reaches deal to buy AstraZeneca's COVID-19 vaccine candidate: media|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-southkorea-vaccine-idUSKBN28D0KI|accessdate=2021-01-05|archivedate=2021-01-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130224712/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-southkorea-vaccine-idUSKBN28D0KI|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Cha S|date=2021-01-04|title=S.Korea reviews AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine, expands ban on gatherings|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-southkorea-astraze-idUSKBN2990GM|accessdate=2021-01-05|archivedate=2021-01-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125121721/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-southkorea-astraze-idUSKBN2990GM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿斯利康与[[SK集团|SK生命科学]]公司签署了生产疫苗产品的协议。合作关系要求，SK子公司为本地和全球市场生产疫苗<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Kim YC|date=2020-11-30|title=Korea signs agreement with AstraZeneca for COVID vaccine|work=The Korea Times|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/tech/2020/12/693_300153.html|accessdate=2021-01-30|archivedate=2021-02-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217113612/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/tech/2020/12/693_300153.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月4日，现年82岁的布莱恩·平克（Brian Pinker）成为在临床试验之外，第一个接种牛津-阿斯利康疫苗的人<ref name="Oxford first vac">{{cite news|title=Covid: Brian Pinker, 82, first to get Oxford-AstraZeneca vaccine|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-55525542|publisher=BBC News Online|accessdate=2021-01-04|date=2021-01-04|archivedate=2021-04-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418153403/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-55525542|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月7日，南非政府宣布，已从印度血清研究所获得首批100万剂疫苗，随后在2月又获得了50万剂疫苗<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Felix J|title=SA will get 1{{nbsp}}million doses of Covid-19 vaccine from India this month|url=https://www.news24.com/news24/southafrica/news/breaking-sa-will-get-1-million-doses-of-covid-19-vaccine-from-india-this-month-20210107|accessdate=2021-01-07|work=News24.com|date=2021-01-07|archivedate=2021-01-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126012833/https://www.news24.com/news24/southafrica/news/breaking-sa-will-get-1-million-doses-of-covid-19-vaccine-from-india-this-month-20210107|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后南非政府宣布取消使用该款疫苗，将联系供应商出售给其他非洲国家，并转用强生疫苗<ref name="reutersSA20210321">{{cite web|title=South Africa sells AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccines to other African countries|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-safrica-vaccine-idUSKBN2BD0K4|accessdate=2021-03-23|date=2021-03-21|work=Reuters|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411234308/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-safrica-vaccine-idUSKBN2BD0K4|archivedate=2021-04-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="RFI20210322">{{cite web|title=South Africa gets rid of 1 million AstraZeneca vaccine doses, but why?|url=https://www.rfi.fr/en/africa/20210322-south-africa-gets-rid-of-1-million-surplus-astrazeneca-vaccines-but-why|accessdate=2021-03-23|date=2021-03-22|work=RFI|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404164620/https://www.rfi.fr/en/africa/20210322-south-africa-gets-rid-of-1-million-surplus-astrazeneca-vaccines-but-why|archivedate=2021-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

缅甸与印度血清研究所签署合同，将在2020年12月获得其3000万剂疫苗。从2021年2月起，缅甸将为1500万人提供疫苗<ref>{{cite news|title=Myanmar will get doses for 15 million people this February|url=https://7day.news/301094|accessdate=2021-01-08|work=7day.news|archivedate=2021-01-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111225114/https://7day.news/301094|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月12日，[[欧洲药品管理局|欧洲药品管理局]]（EMA）收到阿斯利康申請有条件销售许可（Conditional Marketing Authorisation，CMA）。EMA的新闻稿称，相关批文件可于1月29日之前发布，然后由[[欧盟委员会|欧盟委员会]]在几天之内就有条件销售许可做出决定<ref name="EMA application">{{cite news|date=12 January 2021|title=EMA receives application for conditional marketing authorisation of COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca|work=European Medicines Agency|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/ema-receives-application-conditional-marketing-authorisation-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca|accessdate=2021-01-12|archivedate=2021-03-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330170415/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/ema-receives-application-conditional-marketing-authorisation-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca|dead-url=no}}</ref>。匈牙利监管机构則未有等待EMA的批准，便单方面批准該疫苗的應用<ref name="hungary">{{cite web|title=Everything You Need to Know About the Oxford-AstraZeneca Vaccine|url=https://hungarytoday.hu/oxford-astrazeneca-vaccine-hungary/|accessdate=2021-04-01|date=2021-01-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129112403/https://hungarytoday.hu/oxford-astrazeneca-vaccine-hungary/|archivedate=2021-01-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月29日，欧洲药品管理局授予该款疫苗有条件销售许可，建议供18岁及以上人士接種<ref name="COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca EPAR" /><ref name="EMA recommendation">{{cite press release|title=EMA recommends COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca for authorisation in the EU|work=European Medicines Agency (EMA)|date=2021-01-29|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/ema-recommends-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-authorisation-eu|accessdate=2021-01-29|archivedate=2021-02-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112216/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/ema-recommends-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-authorisation-eu|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该建议在当天被欧盟委员会接受<ref name="EU PR 20210129" /><ref name="EU UR info">{{cite web|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca|url=https://ec.europa.eu/health/documents/community-register/html/h1529.htm|accessdate=2021-02-18|work=Union Register of medicinal products|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326062904/https://ec.europa.eu/health/documents/community-register/html/h1529.htm|archivedate=2021-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過疫苗的產量卻趕不上歐盟的需求，阿斯利康早在2021年1月22日便表示，疫苗在歐盟的初始供应量将低于預期，原因是受制於比利时Novasep公司的生产问题。此前媒体预测阿斯利康在4月可累計供應欧盟8000万剂疫苗，但到同年3月，供应量仅有3100万剂<ref name="TG20210122">{{cite news|last=Agencies|date=22 January 2021|title=Covid: Oxford/AstraZeneca vaccine delivery to EU to be cut by 60%|accessdate=2021-01-23|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/22/covid-oxfordastrazeneca-vaccine-delivery-to-eu-to-be-cut-by-60|archivedate=2021-04-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412132235/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/22/covid-oxfordastrazeneca-vaccine-delivery-to-eu-to-be-cut-by-60|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿斯利康首席执行官帕斯卡·索里奥特在接受意大利《共和国报》采访时表示，欧盟的接种时间表比原定晚了两个月，他又提及欧洲一家大型工厂的[[细胞培养|细胞培养]]产量较低，影響了疫苗的生產<ref>{{cite web|title=Pascal Soriot: "There are a lot of emotions on vaccines in EU. But it's complicated"|url=https://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2021/01/26/news/interview_pascal_soriot_ceo_astrazeneca_coronavirus_covid_vaccines-284349628/|accessdate=2021-01-27|date=26 January 2021|work=la Repubblica|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415205315/https://www.repubblica.it/cronaca/2021/01/26/news/interview_pascal_soriot_ceo_astrazeneca_coronavirus_covid_vaccines-284349628/|archivedate=2021-04-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《卫报》发表的分析还发现，比利时的一家工厂在[[生物反应器|生物反应器]]的收率太低，并指出建立此种工艺的过程遇到的困难，经常出现产量變異的情况<ref name="Boseley20210126">{{cite news|vauthors=Boseley S|date=2021-01-26|title=Why has AstraZeneca reduced promised vaccine supply to EU and is UK affected?|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2021-01-27|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/26/why-has-astrazeneca-cut-vaccines-to-eu-and-will-it-impact-uk-|archivedate=2021-04-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210408071411/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/26/why-has-astrazeneca-cut-vaccines-to-eu-and-will-it-impact-uk-|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后欧盟对疫苗实施了[[出口管制|出口管制]]。而关于是否将疫苗转移到英国以及是否会中断向北爱尔兰的运送，引起了争议<ref>{{cite web|title=EU tightens vaccine export rules, creates post-Brexit outcry|url=https://apnews.com/article/europe-health-coronavirus-pandemic-19edc409c6f6a1bd31b69f58f5e1a0a6|accessdate=2021-04-01|date=2021-01-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310053539/https://apnews.com/article/europe-health-coronavirus-pandemic-19edc409c6f6a1bd31b69f58f5e1a0a6|archivedate=2021-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月30日，越南卫生部批准阿斯利康疫苗用于越南境内接种。这是越南首款获准使用的2019冠状病毒病疫苗<ref>{{cite web|title=Coronavirus: Week of Jan. 24 to Jan. 30, Vietnam approves AstraZeneca vaccine|url=https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Coronavirus/Coronavirus-Free-to-read/Coronavirus-Week-of-Jan.-24-to-Jan.-30-Vietnam-approves-AstraZeneca-vaccine|accessdate=2021-04-01|last=Nikkei staff writers|work=Nikkei Asia|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420163235/https://asia.nikkei.com/Spotlight/Coronavirus/Coronavirus-Free-to-read/Coronavirus-Week-of-Jan.-24-to-Jan.-30-Vietnam-approves-AstraZeneca-vaccine|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该款疫苗亦在阿根廷<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Laing A|title=Argentine regulator approves AstraZeneca/Oxford COVID-19 vaccine -AstraZeneca|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-argentina-astrazen/argentine-regulator-approves-astrazeneca-oxford-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-idUSKBN29421P|work=Reuters|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-02-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204164357/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-argentina-astrazen/argentine-regulator-approves-astrazeneca-oxford-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-idUSKBN29421P|dead-url=no}}</ref>、孟加拉国<ref>{{cite news|title=Oxford University-Astrazeneca vaccine: Bangladesh okays it for emergency use|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/frontpage/news/oxford-university-astrazeneca-vaccine-bangladesh-okays-it-emergency-use-2022381|accessdate=2021-01-07|work=The Daily Star|date=2021-01-04|archivedate=2021-01-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127070923/https://www.thedailystar.net/frontpage/news/oxford-university-astrazeneca-vaccine-bangladesh-okays-it-emergency-use-2022381|dead-url=no}}</ref>、巴西<ref>{{cite web|title=Anvisa aprova uso emergencial das vacinas CoronaVac e AstraZeneca no Brasil|url=https://noticias.uol.com.br/saude/ultimas-noticias/redacao/2021/01/17/anvisa-aprova-pedido-de-vacina-do-butantan-e-da-fiocruz.htm|accessdate=2021-01-17|date=2021-01-17|work=UOL|language=pt|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406075210/https://noticias.uol.com.br/saude/ultimas-noticias/redacao/2021/01/17/anvisa-aprova-pedido-de-vacina-do-butantan-e-da-fiocruz.htm|archivedate=2021-04-06|dead-url=no|vauthors=Sabóia G, Mazieiro G, de Andrade H, Adorno L|trans-title=Anvisa approves emergency use of the CoronaVac and AstraZeneca vaccines in Brazil}}</ref>、多米尼加<ref name="la-republica-dominicana">{{cite news|title=La República Dominicana aprueba la vacuna de AstraZeneca contra la covid-19|url=https://www.efe.com/efe/america/sociedad/la-republica-dominicana-aprueba-vacuna-de-astrazeneca-contra-covid-19/20000013-4431079|work=Agencia EFE|date=2020-12-31|language=es|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-01-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124151722/https://www.efe.com/efe/america/sociedad/la-republica-dominicana-aprueba-vacuna-de-astrazeneca-contra-covid-19/20000013-4431079|dead-url=no}}</ref>、萨尔瓦多<ref>{{cite news|title=El Salvador greenlights AstraZeneca, Oxford University COVID-19 vaccine|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-el-salvador-vaccin/el-salvador-greenlights-astrazeneca-oxford-university-covid-19-vaccine-idINKBN2942HQ|work=Reuters|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-01-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124151720/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-el-salvador-vaccin/el-salvador-greenlights-astrazeneca-oxford-university-covid-19-vaccine-idINKBN2942HQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>、印度<ref name="INA authorization"/>、马来西亚<ref>{{cite web|title=Malaysia's NPRA Approves AstraZeneca, Sinovac Covid-19 Vaccines|url=https://codeblue.galencentre.org/2021/03/02/malaysias-npra-approves-astrazeneca-sinovac-covid-19-vaccines/|accessdate=2021-03-02|date=2 March 2021|publisher=CodeBlue|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317152926/https://codeblue.galencentre.org/2021/03/02/malaysias-npra-approves-astrazeneca-sinovac-covid-19-vaccines/|archivedate=2021-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>、墨西哥<ref>{{cite news|author=Comisión Federal para la Protección contra Riesgos Sanitarios|title=Autorización Para Uso De Emergencia A Vacuna AstraZeneca COVID-19|url=https://www.gob.mx/cofepris/articulos/autorizacion-para-uso-de-emergencia-a-vacuna-astrazeneca-covid-19|trans-title=Authorization For Emergency Use Of AstraZeneca Covid-19 Vaccine|accessdate=2021-01-07|work=gob.mx|language=es|archivedate=2021-01-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128231455/https://www.gob.mx/cofepris/articulos/autorizacion-para-uso-de-emergencia-a-vacuna-astrazeneca-covid-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>、尼泊尔<ref>{{cite news|title=Nepal approves AstraZeneca COVID vaccine for emergency use – government statement|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/health-coronavirus-nepal/nepal-approves-astrazeneca-covid-vaccine-for-emergency-use-government-statement-idUSKBN29K140|work=Reuters|date=2021-01-15|accessdate=2021-04-01|archivedate=2021-01-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121032646/https://www.reuters.com/article/health-coronavirus-nepal/nepal-approves-astrazeneca-covid-vaccine-for-emergency-use-government-statement-idUSKBN29K140|dead-url=no}}</ref>、巴基斯坦<ref>{{cite news|vauthors=Shahzad A|date=16 January 2021|title=Pakistan approves AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine for emergency use|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-pakistan-astrazene-idUKKBN29L0DO|accessdate=2021-01-16|archivedate=2021-03-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323215410/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-pakistan-astrazene-idUKKBN29L0DO|dead-url=no}}</ref>、菲律宾<ref>{{cite news|date=2021-01-28|title=Philippine regulator approves emergency use of AstraZeneca vaccine|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-philippines-vaccin-idUSKBN29X0CY|accessdate=2021-01-28|6=|archivedate=2021-02-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207113518/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-philippines-vaccin-idUSKBN29X0CY|dead-url=no}}</ref>、斯里兰卡<ref>{{cite web|title=Sri Lanka approves vaccine amid warnings of virus spread|url=https://apnews.com/article/sri-lanka-coronavirus-pandemic-340488c48ab372050825e70e057dd294|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2021-01-22|work=AP NEWS|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129111234/https://apnews.com/article/sri-lanka-coronavirus-pandemic-340488c48ab372050825e70e057dd294|archivedate=2021-01-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>等国家或地区的监管部门获准在当地紧急使用。

2021年2月7日，南非暂停使用阿斯利康疫苗。[[金山大學|金山大學]]的研究人员在点对点分析中说，对于在南非发现的变异病毒来说，两剂疫苗针对轻度和中度感染来说仅提供“最小保护”<ref>{{cite web|title=Latest – Oxford Covid-19 vaccine trial results – Wits University|url=https://www.wits.ac.za/covid19/covid19-news/latest/oxford-covid-19-vaccine-trial-results.html|accessdate=2021-02-08|work=wits.ac.za|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407122343/https://www.wits.ac.za/covid19/covid19-news/latest/oxford-covid-19-vaccine-trial-results.html|archivedate=2021-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=South Africa halts AstraZeneca vaccinations after data shows little protection against mutation|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/07/south-africa-halts-astrazeneca-vaccinations-.html|accessdate=2021-02-08|date=2021-02-07|publisher=CNBC|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209024437/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/07/south-africa-halts-astrazeneca-vaccinations-.html|archivedate=2021-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=南非暂停使用阿斯利康新冠疫苗：抵御变异病毒效果减弱|url=https://www.yicai.com/news/100945547.html|accessdate=2021-03-31|work=海外网|date=2021-02-08|archivedate=2021-02-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213145424/https://www.yicai.com/news/100945547.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。英国广播公司在2021年2月8日的报道中说，世卫组织免疫主任{{le|凯瑟琳·奥布赖恩|Katherine O'Brien}}表示，她认为阿斯利康疫苗对南非变异株可能具有“有意义的影响”，特别是在预防严重疾病方面和死亡<ref name="BBC-2020208a">{{cite news|title=Covid: Boris Johnson 'very confident' in vaccines being used in UK|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-55983453|date=8 February 2021|accessdate=2021-02-09|work=BBC News|archivedate=2021-02-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216120218/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-55983453|dead-url=no}}</ref>。报道还指出，英格兰副首席医学官乔纳森·范塔姆说，威特沃特斯兰德的研究并没有改变他的观点，即阿斯利康疫苗“极有可能”对南非变种的严重疾病产生影响<ref name="BBC-2020208a"/>。

