=== 智利使用情況 ===
智利衛生部在2021年8月3日舉行的記者會上表示，智利在2021年2月至7月間，對860萬名科興疫苗接種者、450萬名接種輝瑞疫苗者和230萬名接種阿斯利康疫苗者，進行統計及分析，中國科興[[克爾來福疫苗|克爾來福疫苗]]的預防有症狀感染的有效率在2021年2月至4月間為67%，但到同年7月檢測時已下挫到58.5%，而[[輝瑞疫苗|輝瑞疫苗]]及阿斯利康在同年7月的有效率分別為87.7%和68.7%，輝瑞疫苗及阿斯利康疫苗的預防重症及死亡的有效率均為98%及100%，同樣比中國科興疫苗高，由於中國科興疫苗的保護力明顯下滑，因此有需要為接種中國科興疫苗的國民追加第三劑疫苗<ref name="科興預防有症狀新冠肺炎為58.5%">{{cite news |title=智利研究 科興預防有症狀新冠肺炎為58.5% 專家指對Delta反應較弱籲打加強針 |url=https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/3023781/%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BD%9C%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2%E6%9C%89%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%82%BA58.5%25%20%20%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%8DDelta%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E8%BC%83%E5%BC%B1%E7%B1%B2%E6%89%93%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E9%87%9D |accessdate=2021-08-06 |work=晴報 |date=2921-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210806082236/https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/3023781/%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BD%9C%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2%E6%9C%89%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%82%BA58.5%25%20%20%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%B0%8DDelta%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E8%BC%83%E5%BC%B1%E7%B1%B2%E6%89%93%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E9%87%9D |archivedate=2021-08-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2021年8月5日，智利總統[[塞巴斯蒂安·皮涅拉|塞巴斯蒂安·皮涅拉]]在電視講話宣布，智利將於8月11日起，為完成接種兩劑中國科興克爾來福疫苗的人群追加接種多一劑阿斯利康疫苗，補針的首批對象是於2021年3月31日前已接種中國科興疫苗的55歲以上公民<ref name="智利打完科興護力太低決追加AZ">{{cite news |title=打完中國科興2劑保護力太低 智利將追加1劑AZ疫苗 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3629154 |accessdate=2021-08-06 |work=自由時報 |date=2021-08-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210806081028/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3629154 |archivedate=2021-08-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 不良反應 ==
{{seealso|2019冠状病毒病疫苗#血栓与低血小板|2019冠状病毒病疫苗#格林－巴利综合征}}
截至2021年3月7日，{{Internal link helper/en|藥品和保健品監管機構|Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency|英国药监局}}表示，牛津-阿斯利康疫苗接种已超过1170万剂次<ref name="yellow20210228">{{cite web|title=Coronavirus Vaccine : Summary of Yellow Card reporting|url=https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/968411/Coronavirus_vaccine_-_summary_of_Yellow_Card_reporting_28.02.21.pdf|accessdate=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316203656/https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/968411/Coronavirus_vaccine_-_summary_of_Yellow_Card_reporting_28.02.21.pdf|archivedate=2021-03-16|dead-url=no|quotation=It is known from the clinical trials that the more common side effects for both vaccines can occur at a rate of more than one in 10 doses (for example, local reactions or symptoms resembling transient flu-like symptoms)}}</ref>。在临床试验中，超过10%的接种者出现过不良反应，其中大多数是轻度的，包括注射部位压痛、注射部位疼痛、头痛、疲劳、肌痛、不适、发热、发冷、关节痛和恶心<ref name="yellow20210228" /><ref name="EMA20210325ANNEX">{{cite web|title=Annex 1: Summary of Product Characteristics|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/documents/product-information/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-epar-product-information_en.pdf|accessdate=2021-03-25|work=European Medicines Agency (EMA)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313142954/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/documents/product-information/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-epar-product-information_en.pdf|archivedate=2021-03-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外有过敏反应的共234例。在所有COVID-19疫苗类型中，疫苗接种者[[贝尔氏麻痹症|贝尔氏麻痹症]]的发生率均不高于自然预期。接种疫苗后不久死亡的有289例，其中大部分是老年人或体弱者，但该数字与预期的偶然死亡率一致，无因果关系<ref name=yellow20210228/>。[[欧洲药品管理局|欧洲药品管理局]]在2021年3月25日发布了直接的医疗保健专业人员通讯稿，表明尽管可能与非常罕见的{{Internal link helper/en|疫苗接種後栓塞和血栓形成事件|Post-vaccination embolic and thrombotic events|低血小板血凝块}}联系在一起，但接种疫苗的好处远远超过了风险，并建议医疗保健专业人员注意{{Internal link helper/en|血栓栓塞|Venous thrombosis}}和{{Internal link helper/en|血小板减少症|Thrombocytopenia}}的迹象<ref name="EMA20210325RISK">{{cite web|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca: Risk of thrombocytopenia and coagulation disorders|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/medicines/dhpc/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-risk-thrombocytopenia-coagulation-disorders|accessdate=2021-03-25|date=2021-03-24|work=European Medicines Agency (EMA)|archive-date=2021-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726010830/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/medicines/dhpc/vaxzevria-previously-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-risk-thrombocytopenia-coagulation-disorders|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DHPC20210325-RISK">{{cite web|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca: Risk of thrombocytopenia and coagulation disorders|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/documents/dhpc/direct-healthcare-professional-communication-dhpc-vaxzevria-previously-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca_en.pdf|accessdate=2021-03-27|work=European Medicines Agency (EMA)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406105214/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/documents/dhpc/direct-healthcare-professional-communication-dhpc-vaxzevria-previously-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca_en.pdf|archivedate=2021-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月13日，欧洲药品管理局称阿斯利康疫苗与血栓形成之间“有可能存在因果关系”<ref name="ema13apr">{{cite web|title=Direct healthcare professional communication (DHPC): Vaxzevria (previously COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca): link between the vaccine and the occurrence of thrombosis in combination with thrombocytopenia|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/documents/dhpc/direct-healthcare-professional-communication-dhpc-vaxzevria-previously-covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca_en-0.pdf|accessdate=2021-04-13|author=Medical Director of AstraZeneca AB|date=13 April 2021|publisher=欧洲药品管理局}}</ref>。4月23日下午，欧洲药品管理局再次认为，阿斯利康疫苗對所有年齡的接種者的益处大於风险<ref>{{cite news|title=欧洲药品管理局仍推荐接种第二剂阿斯利康新冠疫苗|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-23/doc-ikmyaawc1458037.shtml|accessdate=2021-04-24|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424155151/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-23/doc-ikmyaawc1458037.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[新英格兰医学杂志|新英格兰医学杂志]]一篇论文指出，对于50岁以下阿斯利康疫苗接种者，大约在每5万接种者至少会有一次出现血栓的症状。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2109908 |title=Clinical Features of Vaccine-Induced Immune Thrombocytopenia and Thrombosis |access-date=2021-08-13 |archive-date=2021-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211114125946/https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2109908 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 暫停及恢復使用的歷程 ===
2021年2月，奧地利兩名女子接种该疫苗後，發生凝血障礙，其中一人[[死亡|死亡]]，另一人因[[肺栓塞|肺栓塞]]住院治疗，2021年3月3日，奥地利暂停使用有關批次的疫苗<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca: PRAC preliminary view suggests no specific issue with batch used in Austria|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-prac-preliminary-view-suggests-no-specific-issue-batch-used-austria|accessdate=2021-03-16|work=欧洲药品管理局|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413173559/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-prac-preliminary-view-suggests-no-specific-issue-batch-used-austria|archivedate=2021-04-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管尚未确定血栓与接种疫苗的联系<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=AIFA imposes ban of use of AstraZeneca batch. Investigations in progress in coordination with EMA|url=https://aifa.gov.it/-/aifa-dispone-divieto-di-utilizzo-di-un-lotto-astrazeneca-accertamenti-in-corso-in-coordinamento-con-ema|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=意大利药品管理局|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311133032/https://www.aifa.gov.it/-/aifa-dispone-divieto-di-utilizzo-di-un-lotto-astrazeneca-accertamenti-in-corso-in-coordinamento-con-ema|archivedate=2021-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但丹麦<ref name=":4">{{cite news|last1=Noack|first1=Rik|title=Denmark and Norway suspend AstraZeneca covid vaccine over blood clot concerns, even as European regulator maintains it is safe|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/denmark-temporarily-suspends-astrazeneca-vaccine-even-as-european-regulator-maintains-it-is-safe/2021/03/11/d48662e8-8267-11eb-be22-32d331d87530_story.html|work=华盛顿邮报|date=2021-03-11|accessdate=2021-03-16|archive-date=2021-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726010920/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/denmark-temporarily-suspends-astrazeneca-vaccine-even-as-european-regulator-maintains-it-is-safe/2021/03/11/d48662e8-8267-11eb-be22-32d331d87530_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、挪威<ref name=":4"/>、冰岛<ref name=":4"/>、罗马尼亚<ref name=":5">{{cite web|title=Bulgaria, Romania Order Halt to AstraZeneca Vaccines|url=https://balkaninsight.com/2021/03/12/bulgaria-romania-order-halt-to-astrazeneca-vaccines/|accessdate=2021-03-14|date=2021-03-12|last=Gascón Barberá|first=Marcel|work=BalkanInsight.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323113243/https://balkaninsight.com/2021/03/12/bulgaria-romania-order-halt-to-astrazeneca-vaccines/|archivedate=2021-03-23|dead-url=no|location=Bucharest}}</ref>、保加利亚<ref name=":5"/>、爱尔兰<ref>{{cite news|last1=Griffin|first1=Caitlín|date=2021-03-14|title=AstraZeneca vaccinations suspended in Ireland from this morning|language=en|work=爱尔兰观察报|url=https://www.irishexaminer.com/news/arid-40243931.html|accessdate=2021-03-14|archivedate=2021-03-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317223638/https://www.irishexaminer.com/news/arid-40243931.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、意大利<ref name=":3"/>、西班牙<ref>{{Cite news|title=Breaking News: Spain Suspends ALL AstraZeneca Vaccines|url=https://www.euroweeklynews.com/2021/03/15/breaking-news-spain-suspends-all-astrazeneca-vaccines/|work=Euro Weekly News|accessdate=2021-03-16|archivedate=2021-03-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316105412/https://www.euroweeklynews.com/2021/03/15/breaking-news-spain-suspends-all-astrazeneca-vaccines/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、德国<ref>{{Cite news|title=Major European nations suspend use of AstraZeneca vaccine|url=https://apnews.com/article/business-europe-germany-coronavirus-pandemic-0ab2c4fe13370c96c873e896387eb92f|date=2021-03-14|work=美联社|accessdate=2021-03-16|archivedate=2021-04-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413223527/https://apnews.com/article/business-europe-germany-coronavirus-pandemic-0ab2c4fe13370c96c873e896387eb92f|dead-url=no}}</ref>、荷兰<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-03-15|title=Covid-19: Netherlands suspends use of AstraZeneca vaccine|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-56397157|accessdate=2021-03-16|archivedate=2021-04-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415190414/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-56397157|dead-url=no}}</ref>、瑞典<ref name=":6">{{Cite news|title=Sweden is latest country to stop using AstraZeneca vaccine|url=https://apnews.com/article/europe-summits-germany-coronavirus-pandemic-37c3f8fa9523c58576cbff6d9c13a103|date=2021-03-16|work=美联社|accessdate=2021-03-16|archivedate=2021-03-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325022137/https://apnews.com/article/europe-summits-germany-coronavirus-pandemic-37c3f8fa9523c58576cbff6d9c13a103|dead-url=no}}</ref>也暂停了该疫苗的使用，同时等待欧洲药品管理局完成安全审查。印度尼西亚也暂停该疫苗的使用<ref name=":6"/>，以等待世界卫生组织的安全审查。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Menkes: RI Tunda Penggunaan Vaksin Covid-19 AstraZeneca|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2021/03/15/17393151/menkes-ri-tunda-penggunaan-vaksin-covid-19-astrazeneca|accessdate=2021-03-16|date=2021-03-15|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|work=KOMPAS.com|language=id|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316062943/https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2021/03/15/17393151/menkes-ri-tunda-penggunaan-vaksin-covid-19-astrazeneca|archivedate=2021-03-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>欧洲药品管理局早先表示，没有迹象表明疫苗接种引起凝血反应或血栓，且阿斯利康未将其列为疫苗的副作用。根据欧洲药品管理局的数据，在接种疫苗的人群中发生血栓事件的发生率不高于在普通人群中发生的血栓的发生率。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca: PRAC investigating cases of thromboembolic events - vaccine’s benefits currently still outweigh risks - Update|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-prac-investigating-cases-thromboembolic-events-vaccines-benefits|accessdate=2021-03-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420203555/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-prac-investigating-cases-thromboembolic-events-vaccines-benefits|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2021年3月11日，欧盟共500万人接种了疫苗，其中报告了30例血栓栓塞事件。英国药品和保健产品监管局还表示，在使用超过1100万剂后，尚未确认血凝块的报告是由疫苗引起的，并且不会停止接种疫苗<ref name=":6" />。2021年3月12日，世界卫生组织表示尚未发现因果关系，应继续接种疫苗。<ref>{{Cite web|title=WHO backs AstraZeneca COVID vaccine amid clotting concerns; green lights Johnson & Johnson shots|url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2021/03/1087222|accessdate=2021-03-16|date=2021-03-12|work=UN News|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410144912/https://news.un.org/en/story/2021/03/1087222|archivedate=2021-04-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年3月15日，德国联邦疫苗和生物医学研究机构{{le|保罗·埃尔利希研究所|Paul Ehrlich Institute}}发布调查报告表示，在160万次疫苗接种中，发生了7例脑静脉血栓形成并伴有血小板不足的情况，在统计学上显著高于同期在一般人群中发生的病例数<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=Paul-Ehrlich-Institut - News - The Paul-Ehrlich-Institut informs - Temporary Suspension of Vaccination with COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca|url=https://www.pei.de/EN/newsroom/hp-news/2021/210315-pei-informs-temporary-suspension-vaccination-astra-zeneca.html|accessdate=2021-03-16|work=保罗·埃尔利希研究所|language=de|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420132915/https://www.pei.de/EN/newsroom/hp-news/2021/210315-pei-informs-temporary-suspension-vaccination-astra-zeneca.html|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。保罗·埃尔利希研究所据此建议暂时停止接种疫苗，直到欧洲药品管理局完成对案件的审查为止<ref>{{Cite web|title=Paul-Ehrlich-Institut - Homepage - FAQ - Temporary suspension of COVID-19 vaccine AstraZeneca (PDF version)|url=https://www.pei.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/EN/newsroom-en/hp-news/faq-temporary-suspension-astrazeneca.pdf|accessdate=2021-03-17|work=保罗·埃尔利希研究所|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420180958/https://www.pei.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/EN/newsroom-en/hp-news/faq-temporary-suspension-astrazeneca.pdf|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月17日，世界卫生组织发表了关于该疫苗安全性的声明，认为接种该疫苗的益处超过其风险，并建议继续接种该疫苗<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO statement on AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine safety signals|url=https://www.who.int/news/item/17-03-2021-who-statement-on-astrazeneca-covid-19-vaccine-safety-signals|accessdate=2021-03-17|work=世界卫生组织|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420102440/https://www.who.int/news/item/17-03-2021-who-statement-on-astrazeneca-covid-19-vaccine-safety-signals|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年3月19日，[[歐洲藥品管理局|歐洲藥品管理局]]表示經過調查後，認為接種者血栓風險上升與疫苗沒有關聯，阿斯利康疫苗安全有效，好處多於不良反應的風險，推薦繼續使用阿斯利康疫苗。德國、法國及西班牙在內的多個歐盟成員國表示，將會重新啟用阿斯利康疫苗<ref name="歐盟藥品局稱阿斯利康疫苗安全">{{cite news|title=歐盟藥品管理局稱阿斯利康疫苗安全有效 法德等國紛紛恢復接種阿斯利康疫苗|url=https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20210318-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%97%A5%E5%93%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%B7%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%9B%E7%B4%9B%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97|accessdate=2021-03-19|work=法國國際廣播電台|date=2021-03-19|archivedate=2021-03-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319182806/https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20210318-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%97%A5%E5%93%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88-%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%B7%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%9B%E7%B4%9B%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97|dead-url=no}}</ref>。挪威、瑞典和丹麦则表示要等待阿斯利康疫苗更多研究和测试结果出炉之后，再决定是否恢复使用该疫苗。<ref>{{cite web|title=AstraZeneca’s Covid-19 Vaccine Cleared by EU After Blood-Clot Concerns|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/astrazenecas-covid-19-vaccine-is-cleared-by-europe-after-blood-clot-concerns-11616083845|accessdate=2021-03-19|work=華爾街日報|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420081310/https://www.wsj.com/articles/astrazenecas-covid-19-vaccine-is-cleared-by-europe-after-blood-clot-concerns-11616083845|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年3月18日，欧洲药品管理局宣布，在大约2,000万接种疫苗的人中，一般的血液凝结率是正常的，但该局已经确认7例弥散性血管内凝血和18例脑静脉窦血栓形成的个案<ref name=":8">{{cite press release|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca: benefits still outweigh the risks despite possible link to rare blood clots with low blood platelets|work=European Medicines Agency|date=2021-03-18|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-benefits-still-outweigh-risks-despite-possible-link-rare-blood-clots|accessdate=2021-03-18|archivedate=2021-04-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420083152/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-benefits-still-outweigh-risks-despite-possible-link-rare-blood-clots|dead-url=no}}</ref>。虽然血栓与疫苗的因果关系尚未得到证实，但欧洲药品管理局决定进行进一步分析，并告知患者这种罕见综合征的可能性很小<ref name=":8"/>。欧洲药品管理局确认，该疫苗的好处仍然大于风险，建议继续使用<ref name=":8"/><ref name="mindiao">{{cite news|title=民调：欧洲民众对阿斯利康疫苗信任度显著下降|url=https://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/03-23/9438286.shtml|accessdate=2021-04-01|work=中国新闻网|date=2021-03-23|archivedate=2021-03-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324080813/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/03-23/9438286.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，意大利在欧洲药品管理局发表声明后恢复疫苗接种<ref name=":9">{{cite news|last=Picheta|first=Rob|date=2021-03-18|title=EU regulator declares AstraZeneca vaccine safe, but experts fear damage has been done|work=CNN|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/18/europe/ema-astrazeneca-vaccine-blood-clots-decision-intl/index.html|accessdate=2021-03-19|archivedate=2021-04-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420010620/https://www.cnn.com/2021/03/18/europe/ema-astrazeneca-vaccine-blood-clots-decision-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其余大多数欧洲国家也采取了行动，不久后恢复疫苗接种<ref name=":10">{{cite news|date=2021-03-19|title=EU Resets Vaccine Drive After Chaos That May Undermine Trust|work=Bloomberg.com|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-19/eu-seeks-to-reset-vaccine-drive-after-reversing-astrazeneca-ban|accessdate=2021-03-22|archivedate=2021-03-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322095435/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-19/eu-seeks-to-reset-vaccine-drive-after-reversing-astrazeneca-ban|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了向公众保证疫苗的安全性，英国首相[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]和法国总理[[让·卡斯泰|让·卡斯泰]]在欧盟重新启动阿斯利康疫苗接种计划后不久，向媒体现场直播了疫苗接种过程<ref name=":11">{{cite web|title=AstraZeneca: France, UK prime ministers receive vaccine|url=https://www.dw.com/en/astrazeneca-france-uk-prime-ministers-receive-vaccine/a-56924555|accessdate=2021-03-22|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418044856/https://www.dw.com/en/astrazeneca-france-uk-prime-ministers-receive-vaccine/a-56924555|archivedate=2021-04-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月19日，来自挪威[[奥斯陆大学|奥斯陆大学]]的研究團隊和德国[[格賴夫斯瓦爾德大學|格賴夫斯瓦爾德大學]]的研究團隊分别发现，接种阿斯利康疫苗后会触发自身免疫反应，导致接种者脑部出现血栓。奥斯陆大学医院血液学教授霍尔姆表示，他的团队发现接种阿斯利康疫苗后产生的一种抗体，会引发上述不良反应，除了疫苗，没有其他原因可以解释为什么这些人会出现这样的免疫反应。团队同時指出，出现上述并发症的人少之又少，患者在接种疫苗四天后若出现头痛、头晕或视力受损等症状，可通过血液检查快速确认是否出现血栓，若有此异常状况，可在中型医院获得治疗，换言之，民众无须对接种阿斯利康疫苗心存顾虑。<ref>{{cite web|title=Scientists Say They Found Cause of Rare Blood Clotting Linked to AstraZeneca Vaccine|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/scientists-say-they-found-cause-of-blood-clotting-linked-to-astrazeneca-vaccine-11616169108?mod=searchresults_pos5&page=1|accessdate=2021-03-19|work=華爾街日報|language=en}}</ref>

2021年3月23日，据英国[[民意调查|民意调查]]机构舆观公司（YouGov）进行的民调数据显示，部分国家发现接种阿斯利康疫苗后可能出现并发症，已将其停止使用的新闻后，欧洲民众对这款疫苗的信任度显著下降。与2021年2月的问卷相比，法国、德国、意大利和西班牙信任阿斯利康疫苗的民众数量减少，认为其可能不安全<ref name="mindiao"/>。同日，世界衛生組織呼籲對阿斯利康疫苗有安全疑慮的國家，可以將已購入的疫苗轉讓予世衞主導的全球疫苗保障機制（[[COVAX|COVAX]]），因為現在有不少國家極需要這款疫苗<ref name="世衞呼籲轉讓阿斯利康疫苗">{{cite news|title=世衞籲國家把存疑阿斯利康疫苗讓予COVAX|url=https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2744961/all|accessdate=2021-03-24|work=信報|date=2021-03-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324121830/http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2744961/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E7%B1%B2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%8A%E5%AD%98%E7%96%91%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E8%AE%93%E4%BA%88COVAX|archivedate=2021-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。世衞總幹事[[譚德塞|譚德塞]]更稱疫苗研發廠商應以阿斯利康藥廠為榜樣，呼籲疫苗研發廠商都仿效阿斯利康將疫苗專利授予其他藥廠，加速疫苗的生產<ref name="世衞稱阿斯利康是榜樣">{{cite news|title=世衞促藥廠授出疫苗專利 冀增加產量|url=https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2744671/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E4%BF%83%E8%97%A5%E5%BB%A0%E6%8E%88%E5%87%BA%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9+%E5%86%80%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F|accessdate=2021-03-25|work=信報|date=2021-03-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325102313/http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2744671/%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9E%E4%BF%83%E8%97%A5%E5%BB%A0%E6%8E%88%E5%87%BA%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%B0%88%E5%88%A9+%E5%86%80%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E7%94%A2%E9%87%8F|archivedate=2021-03-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月25日，欧洲药品管理局公布修订后的产品信息<ref name="EMA20210325ANNEX"/><ref name="EMA20210325RISK"/><ref name="EMA20210325PR">{{cite press release|title=COVID-19 Vaccine AstraZeneca – Update on ongoing evaluation of blood clot cases|work=European Medicines Agency (EMA)|date=2021-03-25|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-update-ongoing-evaluation-blood-clot-cases|accessdate=2021-03-25|archivedate=2021-04-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413235604/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/news/covid-19-vaccine-astrazeneca-update-ongoing-evaluation-blood-clot-cases|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月26日，法国药品安全局证实，阿斯利康疫苗存在造成非典型血栓的风险。根据ANSM监测数据，法国3月12日至18日有9人在接种阿斯利康疫苗后出现静脉血栓，其中2人死亡。其位置不典型，主要为脑静脉和消化道，这可能与患者血小板减少症或凝血障碍有关。法国卫生当局正在对该案例展开深入临床调查<ref>{{cite news|author1=李宏策|title=法国证实阿斯利康疫苗可造成罕见血栓|url=http://www.stdaily.com/guoji/xinwen/2021-03/29/content_1099815.shtml|accessdate=2021-04-01|work=科技日报|date=2021-03-20|archivedate=2021-03-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331003132/http://www.stdaily.com/guoji/xinwen/2021-03/29/content_1099815.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月29日，加拿大[[爱德华王子岛省|爱德华王子岛省]]宣布，暂停对55岁以下的人士接种该疫苗，以便“在加拿大范围内按年龄和性别详细评估该疫苗的益处和风险”。[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]和[[曼尼托巴省|曼尼托巴省]]也发表了类似的声明<ref>{{Cite web|title=NACI to recommend halting AstraZeneca vaccine for those under 55: source|url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/health/coronavirus/naci-to-recommend-halting-astrazeneca-vaccine-for-those-under-55-source-1.5366808|accessdate=2021-03-29|date=2021-03-29|work=CTV News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329200540/https://www.ctvnews.ca/health/coronavirus/naci-to-recommend-halting-astrazeneca-vaccine-for-those-under-55-source-1.5366808|archivedate=2021-03-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=P.E.I. suspends use of AstraZeneca vaccine for those younger than 55|url=https://atlantic.ctvnews.ca/p-e-i-suspends-use-of-astrazeneca-vaccine-for-those-younger-than-55-1.5366557|accessdate=2021-03-29|date=29 March 2021|work=CTV News Atlantic|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409155305/https://atlantic.ctvnews.ca/p-e-i-suspends-use-of-astrazeneca-vaccine-for-those-younger-than-55-1.5366557|archivedate=2021-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月30日，德国卫生部宣布，该疫苗不适用于60岁及以下的人士<ref>{{Cite web|title=Germany restricts use of AstraZeneca vaccine to over 60s in most cases|url=https://www.dw.com/en/germany-restricts-use-of-astrazeneca-vaccine-to-over-60s-in-most-cases/a-57049301|accessdate=2021-03-30|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=en-GB|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409103949/https://www.dw.com/en/germany-restricts-use-of-astrazeneca-vaccine-to-over-60s-in-most-cases/a-57049301|archivedate=2021-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年4月3日，英國藥物及保健產品管理局表示，在接种1810萬劑阿斯利康疫苗中出现30宗血栓報告，其中7人死亡<ref>{{cite news|title=英国：30人接种阿斯利康疫苗后出现血栓，其中7人死亡|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-03/doc-ikmyaawa5467872.shtml|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=澎湃新闻|date=2021-04-03|archivedate=2021-04-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403123803/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2021-04-03/doc-ikmyaawa5467872.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當局會持續評估這情況，但目前的證據顯示接種這種疫苗帶來的好處仍大於風險<ref name="30宗血栓">{{cite news|title=英打牛津疫苗致30宗血栓 其中7人亡|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/國際/article/20210404/s00014/1617473651364/英打牛津疫苗致30宗血栓-其中7人亡|accessdate=2021-04-04|work=明報|date=2021-04-04|archivedate=2021-04-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404010548/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20210404/s00014/1617473651364/%e8%8b%b1%e6%89%93%e7%89%9b%e6%b4%a5%e7%96%ab%e8%8b%97%e8%87%b430%e5%ae%97%e8%a1%80%e6%a0%93-%e5%85%b6%e4%b8%ad7%e4%ba%ba%e4%ba%a1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

